 of the asset. Strength, Courtesy, Professionalism, Experience, Solidity, Transparency are just some of our characteristics, and we are certain we can make a difference in the real estate auction market, as we represent "determination and security" to achieve the goals of our clients. ____________________________________________________ ASTE PREASTE INVESTIMENTI Srl We operate based on criteria and guidelines strongly focused on the analysis and constant verification of the Structure and its related Organizational Processes, ', 'Celenza Valfortore', 'Foggia', 'puglia', 'via Cairoli no number', 41.5607503, 14.9825429, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33520418/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/28/4b/76/779217984.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/28/4b/76/779217984.webp"]', 34, 'terracedHouse', 'house', 61.0, 100.0, 40.0, 60.0, 60.0, 43.0, 52.0, 159.0, 'Napoli (NAP)', 95.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (118, '32661511', 990000.0, 500.0, 17, 5, 'Casale/cascina in strada Provinciale Campigliola no number', 'In the heart of the beautiful Tuscan Maremma, in the municipality of Manciano, a wonderful farmhouse completely renovated, located just 15 minutes from the regenerating Terme di Saturnia and 20 minutes from the enchanting beaches of Capalbio and the Argentario Coast. Description: The farmhouse is on three levels for about 510 square meters. On the ground floor there is a large and bright living room with fireplace, a large masonry kitchen and another living area with French doors overlooking the surrounding garden. A master bedroom and a bathroom complete the floor. On the second floor a large patio and four double bedrooms, two of them with balconies and two bathrooms. On the top floor a sitting room with private room and bathroom, ideal as a study or guest room. In the basement cellar and garage. The property has a beautiful dèpandance that is located adjacent to the house. Built in 2010, it offers a living room with fireplace, masonry kitchen, a double bedroom and a bathroom, for a total of about 90sqm. Outdoor spaces: The farmhouse is surrounded by about 3000sqm of garden, and double driveway access with automatic gates fully fenced. Complete the property 13 hectares of land, between arable and woodland and access to the lake. Condition and finishes: The property has been completely renovated and is in excellent condition with exposed beams and terracotta floors. It is equipped with a Gas system with fancoil for heating, air conditioning both in the farmhouse and in the dèpandance. There is a pump system that takes water from the property''s pond for irrigation. Potential uses: This property represents a unique opportunity to live in the tranquility of the Tuscan countryside, with all the amenities and beauty of the surrounding area. Excellent as a vacation home and tourist rentals. Location: Its strategic location allows you to enjoy the famous Terme di Saturnia spa, known for its beneficial thermal waters, and the beaches of Capalbio and the Argentario Coast, w', 'Manciano', 'Grosseto', 'toscana', 'strada Provinciale Campigliola no number', 42.481602, 11.5574288, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32661511/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/0a/e7/61/691195684.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/0a/e7/61/691195684.webp"]', 54, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 61.0, 60.0, 40.0, 60.0, 64.0, 66.0, 67.0, 1980.0, 'Roma FCO', 94.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (119, '33649693', 290000.0, 172.0, 11, 2, 'Villa in via Poggio Donato, 10', 'WHO SAID YOU NEED TO ISOLATE YOURSELF TO BREATHE CLEAN AIR?  A POSITION THAT CHANGES THE RULES OF THE GAME  Santa Fiora, nestled in the greenery at the foot of Mount Amiata, is a place where quality of life isn''t an abstract concept, but a daily reality. We''re not talking about a forgotten village, but a vibrant, well-maintained community with services, history, and an authentic community. And just minutes from the center, within a condominium of villas surrounded by greenery, there''s a property that offers it all: space, views, privacy, and comfort.  SPACE FOR YOUR FAMILY... BUT AT WHAT PRICE?  Anyone looking for spacious homes in Tuscany knows it: you''ll only find properties in need of complete renovation, or isolated homes, far from everything. And those in good condition? They''re often too small or lack a view. And if you need more than three bedrooms, you''re done. Or are you?  BEAUTIFUL HOUSES THAT REMAIN IMPOSSIBLE  Even when you find the right house, you discover it lacks a garage, the garden is neglected, or worse: it needs work everywhere. And then doubts, costs, and sacrifices pile up. But this time, the right house already exists.  A COMPLETE, INDEPENDENT, READY-MADE VILLA  We''re talking about almost 200 m² of living space, with five bedrooms, a separate studio apartment, two bathrooms, a large living room, a study, an eat-in kitchen, and three panoramic southwest-facing balconies with unobstructed views of the Maremma. On clear days, you can even see Monte Argentario on the horizon, and even a glimpse of the sea in the distance.  And that''s not all: you have an internally connected garage, a 35 m² cellar, and 1,470 m² of private garden that embraces the entire house.  The building dates back to the 1970s, but the roof was recently redone, all the plumbing and electrical systems are new from 2023, and the structure is in excellent condition.  This isn''t just a spacious home: it''s energy self-sufficient. Thanks to a 6.9 kW photovoltaic system with battery,', 'Santa Fiora', 'Grosseto', 'toscana', 'via Poggio Donato, 10', 42.8405134, 11.6235346, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33649693/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/36/48/fe/725503985.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/36/48/fe/725503985.webp"]', 50, 'villa', 'villa', 61.0, 73.0, 40.0, 40.0, 64.0, 51.0, 70.0, 1686.0, 'Firenze (FLR)', 113.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (120, '35125354', 72000.0, 65.0, 3, 1, 'Detached house in via Is Ammostus, 2', 'In Quartu Sant’Elena, on Via Is Ammostus, we offer for sale a detached house that represents a solution for those who wish to create a tailor-made living project. The property, with 65 commercial square meters, is completely to be renovated and requires a comprehensive redevelopment intervention, a condition that makes it particularly interesting for those looking for a property to transform and personalize according to their needs. The property is spread over the ground floor and has three rooms, a bathroom, a kitchenette, and south-east exposure. The real strong point, however, is the outdoor space: the house is set on a plot with a private garden of approximately 1,200 sq m, as well as a veranda, a terrace, a driveway courtyard, and an uncovered parking space. A configuration that offers great potential, especially for those looking for a detached house to restore in Quartu Sant’Elena, enhancing the internal spaces and open areas. It is therefore a proposal suitable for those who are not looking for a ready-to-live-in property, but a detached house entirely to be renovated, with ample possibilities for reinterpretation and development. The location in Quartu Sant’Elena adds further interest to a solution that can express its full value through a complete renovation intervention.', 'Quartu Sant''Elena', 'Cagliari', 'sardegna', 'via Is Ammostus, 2', 39.2461123, 9.2335446, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/35125354/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/44/3f/0a/780997957.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/44/3f/0a/780997957.webp"]', 29, 'independantHouse', 'house', 61.0, 88.0, 40.0, 100.0, 56.0, 45.0, 52.0, 1108.0, 'Cagliari (CAG)', 15.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (121, '35015828', 39000.0, 198.0, 9, 1, 'Detached house in via Gabriele D''Annunzio', 'Magomadas, an ancient and typical village with character located on the central western coast of Sardinia, at just 5 minutes to the beach and 10 minutes to the wonderful medieval Town of Bosa and its stunning coves with crystal-clear waters; we offer for sale this property that offers a unique opportunity for those seeking peace and natural beauty. Nestled in a quiet area with no traffic, it is the ideal retreat for those wishing to escape the hustle and bustle of everyday life. This two floor house is in need of renovation and offers a living space of 198 sqm. On the ground floor there is a large entrance hall and a spacious living room, a kitchen-dining room, a hallway, a bathroom, and a veranda overlooking a private garden with beautiful panoramic views. On the first floor, four spacious and well-lit bedrooms guarantee comfort and space for the entire family. With considerable potential for renovation and modernization, this house represents an ideal investment for those wishing to personalize their living space. Don''t miss the opportunity to transform this property into a corner of paradise.', 'Magomadas', 'Oristano', 'sardegna', 'via Gabriele D''Annunzio', 40.2649719, 8.5210374, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/35015828/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/79/42/98/777999245.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/79/42/98/777999245.webp"]', 29, 'independantHouse', 'villa', 61.0, 100.0, 40.0, 40.0, 56.0, 50.0, 58.0, 197.0, 'Olbia (OLB)', 110.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
