 management of the asset. Strength, Courtesy, Professionalism, Experience, Solidity, Transparency are just some of our characteristics and we are certain to make a difference in the real estate auction market, as we represent "determination and security" to achieve the goals of our clients. ____________________________________________________ ASTE PREASTE INVESTIMENTI Srl We operate on the basis of criteria and guidelines strongly focused on the analysis and constant verification of the Structure and its related Organiza', 'Uras', 'Oristano', 'sardegna', 'via Eleonora, 33', 39.6968768, 8.7026722, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34048972/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/52/ff/aa/774388551.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/52/ff/aa/774388551.webp"]', 38, 'independantHouse', 'house', 61.0, 100.0, 40.0, 80.0, 56.0, 39.0, 52.0, 132.0, 'Cagliari (CAG)', 58.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (123, '32200002', 450000.0, 308.0, 8, 4, 'Casale/cascina', 'BETWEEN SESTOLA AND FANANO – at 900 meters above sea level, in a unique position with stunning views of Mount Cimone and the surrounding valley, we offer a beautiful estate surrounded by 40,000 sqm of land in a single plot, including meadows and woodland, the result of a meticulous renovation. The main residence is a generously sized stone farmhouse dating back to 1880, featuring spacious and open interiors. It consists of a large living room with an original antique fireplace at its center, an extremely spacious kitchen, and a bathroom on the ground floor. On the upper floors, there are five bedrooms, each with its own bathroom. The property has been completely renovated over the past five years. The second building, also of substantial size, is a former stone barn converted into a large garage with bathroom-laundry area. The former stable has been fully restored using the original materials, and above it there is a covered portico that can accommodate 4–5 cars. The property is completed by an ancient metato (traditional chestnut drying house) with a restored original stone oven and grill. A natural spring is present on the property in addition to the municipal water supply. All utilities are connected. Systems are fully compliant with current regulations.', 'Fanano', 'Modena', 'emilia-romagna', 'Fanano', 44.2287903, 10.8186047, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32200002/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/0f/1e/b6/676804181.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/0f/1e/b6/676804181.webp"]', 34, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 61.0, 59.0, 40.0, 80.0, 56.0, 62.0, 69.0, 1461.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 51.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (124, '34351335', 198000.0, 187.0, 3, 2, 'Semi-detached house in via Pietro Bacchi, 5 /a', 'In the heart of Bagnara di Romagna, we offer a portion of an independent ground-to-sky house, completely renovated and ready to be inhabited. A solution that offers the convenience of the center at your fingertips and zero renovation costs. On the ground floor you will find a welcoming entrance, a large and bright living room, kitchenette, dining room, full bathroom and a garage for one car, ideal for those who want functionality and parking convenience. The sleeping area is instead developed on the first floor with two double bedrooms, a single room/study and a bathroom with shower. Further predisposition for a bathroom or space that can be used as a walk-in closet. There is also a connection to the attic floor, now used as a convenient storage room but easily enhanced. A well-kept, complete and ready-to-live-in house, perfect for those looking for space and autonomy with the charm of life in the historic center. Asking price €198,000. 00. More info at reference 2253 on Your new home in Bagnara is waiting for you, contact us now!', 'Bagnara di Romagna', 'Ravenna', 'emilia-romagna', 'via Pietro Bacchi, 5 /A', 44.3892078, 11.8274278, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34351335/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/40/ce/3a/751275615.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/40/ce/3a/751275615.webp"]', 43, 'semidetachedHouse', 'house', 61.0, 84.0, 40.0, 80.0, 56.0, 40.0, 65.0, 1059.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 46.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (125, '35123883', 430000.0, 666.0, 13, 4, 'Estate in contrada Salci Capretta', 'Are you looking for a comfortable farmhouse in a flat area close to cafes and delicious pizzerias? Here is an attractive, habitable stone farmhouse in vintage style, featuring a living area and 7 bedrooms, as well as a basement level ideal for a traditional tavern and a detached outbuilding for a guest annex. There is the possibility to restore 2 apartments. Surrounded by approximately 1 hectare of land where you can create a beautiful garden and a swimming pool. Habitable and functional, bright with large windows and a terrace; it features external stone walls and a roof with red tiles. Inside, there are high-quality single-fired ceramic floors and parquet flooring in the bedrooms. Wooden window frames with double glazing. Mosquito screens on the ground floor. External wooden shutters. On the first floor, 2 bathrooms with bathtub and shower and 1 bathroom with shower only. On the ground floor, a guest bathroom. Potential enhancements to make it more traditional and possibility for a swimming pool. All utilities are in place, with connection to the public aqueduct and a private well. LPG heating system with 2 boilers (one per floor), plus a pellet stove on the ground floor. 2 wood-burning fireplaces. Possibility to install solar and photovoltaic panels. Potential thanks to its convenient and strategic location at the crossroads of three regions: Umbria, Lazio and Tuscany, the property is habitable and fully functional, ideal both as a private residence and as a hospitality structure (B&B), with ample scope for customization to enhance its characteristic style. Possibility of 2 apartments with independent entrances and a guesthouse in the annex. Generous spaces such as the basement level and the annex can be further optimized. An attractive investment opportunity with potential for continued short- or long-term rental income. In Umbria, bordering Tuscany, with direct access from a paved road, set in a convenient and flat area with no unpaved roads, steep descents, or', 'Fabro', 'Terni', 'umbria', 'contrada Salci Capretta', 42.8718042, 12.004515, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/35123883/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/39/7a/0d/780962008.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/39/7a/0d/780962008.webp"]', 41, 'countryHouse', 'farmhouse', 61.0, 85.0, 15.0, 40.0, 54.0, 70.0, 70.0, 646.0, 'Roma FCO', 121.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (126, '32442765', 675000.0, 816.0, 26, 3, 'Detached house in strada Burra', 'Stunning Brick Farmhouse in the Asti Countryside! Discover the timeless charm of this beautifully restored stone farmhouse in the heart of the Asti countryside, where history and elegance seamlessly intertwine. This century-old property is brimming with original features, from exposed brick walls and meticulously restored frescoes to the iconic vaulted ceilings. The estate even boasts a traditional wine cellar, complete with original barrels (botti) once used for producing, aging, and storing wine — a true homage to the area’s rich winemaking heritage. The farmhouse has been tastefully renovated with high-quality materials, preserving its historical character while adding modern comforts. Stepping inside, you’re immediately enveloped in warmth and charm, as the property’s unique blend of tradition and sophistication welcomes you home. The enchanting garden, lush with greenery, features a fully equipped outdoor kitchen and dining area — perfect for leisurely meals with friends and family. As you enter the ground floor through a picturesque gallery porch, you’ll find a spacious entryway leading to a kitchen and bathroom, along with three additional rooms that offer endless potential. This section of the home which still needs to be completed, could easily be transformed into a delightful guesthouse or private dependance. The newer wing of the property is a stunning fusion of old and new, featuring an expansive open-concept living kitchen. The space is highlighted by exposed brick vaulted ceilings and is fully equipped with appliances and large counter space to cater to all your culinary endeavors. Adjacent to the kitchen, a convenient storage room sits next to an elegant formal dining room, where antique furnishings, intricate frescoes, and a wood-burning fireplace create a captivating atmosphere. A living room and an elegant studio complete the ground floor. Upstairs, a grand staircase leads to the first floor, where you’ll find 4 sunlit bedrooms, a cozy living room,', 'Antignano', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'strada Burra', 44.8432125, 8.1356421, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32442765/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/1f/60/55/712156118.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/1f/60/55/712156118.webp"]', 64, 'independantHouse', 'farmhouse', 61.0, 75.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 72.0, 66.0, 827.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 55.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (127, '29912743', 194000.0, 239.0, 10, 2, 'Casale/cascina in via Dottor Giuseppe Ollino', 'A classical and typical farmhouse in exposed brick, dating back to the early 20th century and still with its original vaulted ceiling and the magnificent vaulted cellar!  The building is independent on 4 sides, located between the hamlet of Santa Caterina and the centre of Rocca d''Arazzo, the position is hilly, sunny and enjoys a fabulous view of the Alps.  Basement floor: the classic cantina with brick barrel  Ground floor: Entrance into staircase, spacious living room with decorated ceiling, kitchen, diningroom, bathroom and large storage room/garage in the original stables  First floor: 3 bedrooms, balcony, hallway, bathroom and spacious storage room (former barn).  The property is completed by a large garden-courtyard of 820 sqm and included in the sale, further land not adjoining but in Rocca d''Arazzo of 17,897 sqm.', 'Rocca d''Arazzo', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'via Dottor Giuseppe Ollino', 44.8488943, 8.2675361, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/29912743/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f3/32/76/773808106.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f3/32/76/773808106.webp"]', 58, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 61.0, 76.0, 15.0, 60.0, 54.0, 64.0, 76.0, 812.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 62.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (128, '33924649', 1150000.0, 200.0, 7, 4, 'Villa in contrada Lamacoppa no number', 'Villa with Pool and Trullo a short distance from Ostuni Discover this splendid villa with pool and trullo in Ostuni, an oasis of elegance and relaxation immersed in the Apulian countryside, just a few minutes from the center of the White City. The property combines the charm of tradition with the ultimate in modern comfort, offering a unique and complete living experience. Main features: Spacious and bright living area, with elegant open space living 4 bedrooms: three in the main unit with vaulted ceilings and precious Trani floors, one in the outbuilding with typical Apulian trullo Private swimming pool of 40 square meters, perfectly integrated into the surrounding landscape Equipped kitchen 2 washing machines, also ideal for receptive use or large family Air conditioning throughout the house and also in the trullo 5 custom-made wardrobes for optimal space management Technology and comfort: 14 kW photovoltaic system and storage battery for significant energy savings Starlink Internet connection, ideal for smart working and streaming Video surveillance system with 3 cameras and alarm system Water softener and filter, for always pure water Outdoor spaces and nature: Land with 50 new olive trees, all served by automatic irrigation system Well-kept garden with irrigation system 2 false pepper trees, ideal for creating natural shade areas Custom-made curtains and pleated blinds in every room, for elegance and privacy Land description: The surrounding land measures 9,622 square meters. Possible developments: This villa is the ideal solution for those looking for an exclusive private residence in Puglia, or an investment for high-level tourist rentals. The perfect mix of rustic charm and technological innovation.', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'contrada Lamacoppa no number', 40.696137, 17.5771628, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33924649/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f7/76/81/735216729.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f7/76/81/735216729.webp"]', 51, 'villa', 'trullo', 60.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 69.0, 88.0, 5750.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 84.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (129, '34252720', 850000.0, 500.0, 10, 10, 'Detached house in strada Provinciale Montemassi no number', 'YOUR BUSINESS STARTS HERE: LIVE, HOST, EARN  INSTANT INCOME IN TUSCANY  Maremma isn''t just a landscape: it''s a vibrant market. Nestled between rolling hills and coastal breezes, this property offers you an immediate income stream, fully organized and ready to go from day one. Here, quality of life and financial returns go hand in hand.  WHERE DEMAND MEETS EXPERIENCE  The area attracts tourists seeking authenticity combined with comfort: well-appointed accommodations, local cuisine, outdoor spaces, and azure waters just minutes away. In this setting, having a fully equipped facility means embracing the season, long weekends, private events, and the slow winter season of food, wine, and wellness.  THE INVISIBLE COST OF “ALMOST READY”  The market is full of properties that are attractive on paper but slow to put into practice. Between permits, suppliers, and unexpected events, the summer flies by and capital remains parked. Every month lost is margin that disappears, while those who are operational cash in and retain customers.  LONG TIME, HIGH RISK  Starting from scratch means managing construction sites, waiting times, and energy-draining technical decisions. And when you finally open, the season is already half over. A smart investor prefers a solid and versatile foundation, with a clear identity and standards already aligned with guests'' expectations.  THREE ACTIVITIES, ONE DIRECTOR  Here you''ll find a main house with three bedrooms and a scenic living room, perfect as an owner''s residence or management headquarters. Adjacent, six bedrooms, each with a private bathroom, sleep eleven, ready to accommodate couples, families, and small groups. The fully equipped restaurant is ideal for experiential dinners, intimate events, or a separate management structure that generates a constant flow of guests. The large, focal point of the outdoor hospitality experience is the pool, while the hectare of flat land opens up to additional formats: a gourmet vegetable garden for the', 'Roccastrada', 'Grosseto', 'toscana', 'strada Provinciale Montemassi no number', 42.9923695, 11.0606409, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34252720/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/c0/8e/5f/747149913.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/c0/8e/5f/747149913.webp"]', 55, 'independantHouse', 'house', 60.0, 73.0, 40.0, 60.0, 64.0, 50.0, 60.0, 1700.0, 'Firenze (FLR)', 92.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (130, '34111734', 598000.0, 220.0, 8, 2, 'Villa in via Fungiaia', 'The Tuscan Dream: Charming Villa with Pool and Absolute Privacy in the Pisan Hills Nestled in the tranquillity of the Pisan hills, strategically located a short distance from the most iconic art cities and the coast, this magnificent villa represents the quintessence of the Tuscan lifestyle. A charming residence in a dominant, panoramic position, surrounded by 1.7 hectares (4.2 acres) of private parkland, where privacy is absolute, yet only minutes from all amenities. The property, spanning approximately 220 sqm (2,368 sqft), has been tastefully restored, preserving its authentic rustic style: terracotta floors, ceilings with exposed beams and tiles, and elegant country-chic furnishings. Flexibility and Style The villa currently offers unique flexibility, being divided into two independent living units—ideal for hosting friends and family or for two separate households—but can be easily combined into one single, prestigious residence. The Main Apartment (Ground Floor): Opens into an intimate entrance hall with a fireplace, leading to the spacious living area. The eat-in kitchen, the convivial heart of the home, has direct access to the magnificent poolside pergola: the perfect setting for unforgettable summer dinners. The sleeping area includes two large bedrooms, a study, and a sumptuous master bathroom with exposed beams, equipped with both a hot tub and a shower. The Guest Apartment (First Floor): A cozy, independent unit featuring a traditional masonry kitchen, a living room, two further bedrooms, and a bathroom. Exteriors, Pool, and Privacy The true luxury of the property is its 1.7-hectare private park. The gently sloping land, completely fenced, ensures an oasis of peace and includes a manicured garden surrounding the house, an olive grove, woodland, and arable land. The splendid swimming pool, located just off the living area and framed by greenery, offers moments of pure relaxation and conviviality. Access, via a white road kept in perfect condition, adds t', 'Crespina Lorenzana', 'Pisa', 'toscana', 'via Fungiaia', 43.5704324, 10.5564096, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34111734/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/9a/a0/95/741916867.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/9a/a0/95/741916867.webp"]', 55, 'villa', 'villa', 60.0, 26.0, 40.0, 100.0, 64.0, 72.0, 73.0, 2718.0, 'Pisa (PSA)', 18.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (131, '31249144', 169000.0, 135.0, 4, 3, 'Terraced house in via Argine a Destra del Parma, 24', 'COPPER: We offer for sale a portion of a head house, immersed in the tranquility of the countryside and surrounded by about 5000 square meters of agricultural land. Located in a characteristic context in the courtyard, this property guarantees serenity and total privacy. In addition to the reserved position, what makes this property unique are the various accessories at the service of the house, such as the 26 sqm garage and a 72 sqm warehouse, ideal for those who need extra space. The house is on three levels. On the ground floor there is a welcoming living room with an elegant wood-burning fireplace, exposed beams and a charming brick arch, which create a rustic and refined atmosphere. The kitchen is large and habitable. The floor is completed by a bathroom with shower and a practical pantry / closet / laundry area. The sleeping area, located on the first floor, houses two double bedrooms, one with a walk-in closet, and a bathroom with a bathtub. On the second floor, finally, there is a spacious and versatile attic, with a dedicated bathroom and a large open space environment that lends itself to multiple uses, adapting to any need. This property is ideal for a family and for those who love to look out and admire the beauty of the countryside, enjoying a relaxing view immersed in the green every day.', 'Colorno', 'Parma', 'emilia-romagna', 'via Argine a Destra del Parma, 24', 44.9359119, 10.4063076, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/31249144/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/92/fb/0b/770732470.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/92/fb/0b/770732470.webp"]', 33, 'terracedHouse', 'house', 60.0, 72.0, 40.0, 60.0, 56.0, 48.0, 69.0, 1252.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 83.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (132, '33845101', 365000.0, 265.0, 6, 2, 'Villa in strada Villanova Superiore, 149', 'In a quiet and well-connected area of Bagnacavallo, we present an ECLECTIC AND COMPLETELY RENOVATED VILLA, ideal for those seeking ample space, modern comfort, and the serenity of living in an independent house. Spread over two levels, the house offers WELCOMING AND WELL-ORGANIZED ROOMS: on the ground floor, you will find a eat-in kitchen, a bright dining room, a spacious living room, a full bathroom with a shower, and finally, a laundry room essential for domestic life. The sleeping area is located on the first floor with three bedrooms, a second bathroom, and A TERRACE THAT OFFERS PRIVACY AND NATURAL LIGHT. Outside, a LARGE GARDEN at the back becomes the perfect space for outdoor dining, moments of relaxation, or family games. The PAVED COURTYARD WITH A PERGOLA adds practicality and aesthetic care, making this property functional in every detail. Completely renovated in 2011, THE VILLA IS READY TO BE LIVED IN, GIVING YOU THE CHARM OF INDEPENDENCE AND THE CONVENIENCE OF A MODERN HOME. Asking price €365,000. Don''t miss out, search for reference 2257 on.', 'Bagnacavallo', 'Ravenna', 'emilia-romagna', 'strada Villanova Superiore, 149', 44.441427, 12.0478165, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33845101/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a9/92/b6/743957839.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a9/92/b6/743957839.webp"]', 27, 'villa', 'villa', 60.0, 64.0, 40.0, 60.0, 56.0, 53.0, 73.0, 1377.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 61.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (133, '30953131', 195000.0, 217.0, 8, 2, 'Casale/cascina in località Boschetto, 1', 'Typical Piedmontese farmhouse in Cissone in Alta Langa We offer for sale a typical Piedmontese farmhouse in Cissone in Alta Langa. Don''t miss this extraordinary opportunity! The typical Piedmontese farmhouse, free on four sides on a plot of approximately 1800 sqm, consists of a residential part and a part with accessory rooms once used for the farm. The farmhouse can be used as a primary residence or as a holiday home. The large size and the simple rectangular structure allow for easy transformation into a hospitality facility with the possibility of creating a B&B or more independent apartments for rent. Alta Langa is one of the most sought-after areas for food and wine tourism, with a growing demand for accommodation facilities. A large flat courtyard and the adjoining land offer ample possibilities for the creation of a swimming pool, a furnished garden, or an outdoor relaxation area. The Dotta real estate agency has stood out for years in the local market thanks to the extreme seriousness and competence of its staff. It is part of our mission to accompany the client in the process of evaluating and choosing the property that best suits their expectations and needs. Contact us immediately to view this house in the Langhe together. We will be happy to accompany you to the property without any obligation, with courtesy and professionalism.', 'Cissone', 'Cuneo', 'piemonte', 'località Boschetto, 1', 44.5521607, 8.0084032, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/30953131/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f5/89/1c/638143060.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f5/89/1c/638143060.webp"]', 25, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 60.0, 68.0, 15.0, 60.0, 54.0, 64.0, 76.0, 899.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 68.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (134, '32138497', 435000.0, 600.0, 10, 8, 'Casale/cascina in Borgata Garombo, 10', 'Hospitality structure in Alta Langa. Somano D647.23. We offer for sale a renovated hospitality structure in 2013 in a rustic style in a panoramic position in Alta Langa. The hospitality structure is on two levels, distributed as follows: lounge, kitchen, bathrooms and various rooms serving the restaurant on the ground floor; mini apartment and four bedrooms with bathroom on the first floor. The property includes the garden, parking for guests and a beautiful panoramic terrace. The property includes 7,000 square meters of agricultural land, mostly woodland. The hospitality structure in Alta Langa is ideal for those who wish to start a business in the agricultural sector or for anyone interested in investing in a stable and profitable sector. Possibility of purchasing an additional building to be renovated with a relevant garden in the village. The Dotta real estate agency has distinguished itself for years in the territorial panorama thanks to the extreme seriousness and competence of the staff. It is part of our mission to accompany the client in the process of evaluating and choosing the property that best suits their expectations and needs. Contact us now to view this house in the Langhe together. We will be happy to accompany you to the property without any obligation, with courtesy and professionalism.', 'Somano', 'Cuneo', 'piemonte', 'Borgata Garombo, 10', 44.5372515, 8.030758, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32138497/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/8e/90/4a/674624137.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/8e/90/4a/674624137.webp"]', 26, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 60.0, 84.0, 15.0, 60.0, 54.0, 59.0, 68.0, 725.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 65.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (135, '32612578', 95000.0, 614.0, 18, 2, 'Village house in via Roma', 'In the small village of Castelletto Molina, in the province of Asti (Piedmont), we are offering for sale a 614 sqm property complex located in the center of the town! Ground floor: living room, 2 kitchens, lounge, bedroom, unfinished attic space, woodshed, 5 storage rooms, and a 74 sqm warehouse. First floor: 3 storage rooms, hallway, 6 bedrooms, and 2 bathrooms. Second floor: 4 bedrooms. The urban plot is 950 sqm! The location is ideal, halfway between Nizza Monferrato and Acqui Terme! The property is ideal for hospitality use or as a multi-family residence!', 'Castelletto Molina', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'via Roma', 44.7530288, 8.4360507, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32612578/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/1a/21/02/689594253.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/1a/21/02/689594253.webp"]', 74, 'casaDePueblo', 'villa', 60.0, 100.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 47.0, 57.0, 155.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 49.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (136, '34873965', 419000.0, 401.0, 10, 3, 'Villa in via Roma', 'Panoramic Villa Amid the Hills of Monferrato! In the heart of Monferrato, among gentle hills and rarefied silences, this property blends naturally into a landscape of remarkable harmony. Its panoramic location offers sweeping views of greenery and the Monviso, creating a constant dialogue between architecture and nature. The villa features clean, contemporary lines with light-colored facades and a pitched roof, welcoming bright and well-proportioned interiors where modern style meets the warmth of exposed brick, bringing continuity and character to every space. The interior spaces are spread over multiple levels and designed to offer comfort, privacy, and maximum flexibility across three floors: Basement: utility room – boiler room – cellar – garage – bathroom – hallway – two spacious rooms ideal for a tavern or relaxation area. Ground floor: welcoming entrance opening directly onto a living room with a large window framing the Alps – bright, fully equipped kitchen with breathtaking views, connected to a wide portico that provides an ideal architectural solution for those who love entertaining and outdoor living, extending the home’s usable space during the warmer months – hallway – two large bedrooms – bathroom. First floor: airy hallway – two bedrooms, one of which opens onto a covered terrace that extends the living space, creating an intimate and protected environment – bathroom – large attic room with a height of 2.15 m. Outside, the garden surrounds the house in complete privacy and offers the potential for a swimming pool, perfect for enjoying outdoor living in the warmer seasons. This property is ideal for those seeking a prestigious residence, a multi-family home, or an exclusive vacation retreat in an area where tranquility and convenience intertwine.', 'Vigliano d''Asti', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'via Roma', 44.833067, 8.2328814, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34873965/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/60/5c/5f/773803043.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/60/5c/5f/773803043.webp"]', 65, 'villa', 'villa', 60.0, 55.0, 15.0, 60.0, 72.0, 66.0, 71.0, 1045.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 61.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (137, '33348121', 485000.0, 450.0, 16, 6, 'Casale/cascina in E70', 'Located in the hills of the Monferrato, this typical L-shaped Piedmontese farmhouse dating back to the 1700s (approximately 450 sqm) features a large internal courtyard garden, accessed through a charming double entrance for vehicles and pedestrians. The main residential unit consists of: Ground floor, overlooking the internal courtyard-garden: an entrance/hallway, a sitting room, a functional kitchen (furnished and included in the price) with an island, a pantry, a large and bright living room, a hallway/anteroom, a bathroom, and the cellar (a tavern-style room with a furnished kitchen included in the price). Ground floor, overlooking the rear courtyard: a veranda, a woodshed, a bathroom, a boiler room, a technical room for the heating system, and a spacious storage area for machinery and agricultural equipment. First floor: 3 bedrooms with separate access, 3 bathrooms, a characteristic hayloft (open portico) with 3 classic exposed brick arches, 2 terraces and a balcony that enjoy a splendid panoramic view. On the right side of the main house, overlooking the internal courtyard-garden, there is a functional dépendance (an excellent, very new building currently used as a workshop) consisting of 3 rooms, 3 bathrooms and a storage room. Opposite the main house, overlooking the internal courtyard-garden, there is a classic independent rustic outbuilding, with a portico on the ground floor and a hayloft on the first floor. The land, in a single plot along with the buildings, totaling 27,320 sqm (currently used as meadowland). Distances from the property: 1.5 km from the village center of Cortandone (AT), 13 km from the Asti Ovest exit of the Turin–Piacenza motorway, 12 km from the Golf Feudo di Asti courses, 37 km from Alba and 45 km from Turin. In addition to being used as a single-family or two-family home, the property is also suitable for an agriturismo, B&B, farmstay, educational farm and/or equestrian facility. Features: Solar panels for hot water production Plumb', 'Asti', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'E70', 44.9159037, 8.2157997, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33348121/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a8/13/28/714656717.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a8/13/28/714656717.webp"]', 148, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 60.0, 52.0, 15.0, 80.0, 72.0, 59.0, 71.0, 1078.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 55.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (138, '30504905', 239000.0, 300.0, 10, 2, 'Casale/cascina in Regione San Rocco', 'The property is located in the heart of the Monferrato hills, a UNESCO World Heritage Site, just 1.5 km from the centre of Montegrosso d''Asti and a couple of kilometres from the renowned town of Agliano Terme.  It is surrounded by lush vineyards and enjoys a lovely view over the hillside.  The farmhouse, in need of modernisation, is about 300 square metres and can also be used for more families, accommodation, bed and breakfast and/or riding stables. It is independent on 4 sides and has a courtyard of 710 sqm.  The property is completed by another 5,340 sqm of land adjacent to the building.  - Basement floor: large storage room and classic cellar. - Ground floor: entrance hall, kitchen, 2 large bedrooms, hallway, bathroom, boiler room and 3 large storage rooms. - First floor: 3 bright rooms, hallway, bathroom, 2 balconies and 3 spacious storage rooms.', 'Agliano Terme', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'Regione San Rocco', 44.803273, 8.2439105, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/30504905/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/c1/74/ee/773786580.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/c1/74/ee/773786580.webp"]', 72, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 60.0, 78.0, 15.0, 60.0, 54.0, 53.0, 75.0, 797.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 64.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (139, '33368338', 220000.0, 270.0, 9, 1, 'Villa in via Montegrappa', 'Spacious house with panoramic terrace, rustic portion and private garden – Village of Miogliola In the charming village of Miogliola, a few steps from the historic little church, we offer for sale a large property consisting of two adjacent buildings: a residential part dating back to the 1960s and a very old rustic portion, both surrounded by a private garden. The main house is spread over three levels: • Ground floor: large garage, two cellars and technical room. • First floor: apartment consisting of kitchen, living room, three bedrooms, bathroom and access to a splendid panoramic terrace overlooking the village. • Attic: large recoverable space, ideal for creating additional rooms. The rustic portion, on two levels, is to be renovated and offers the possibility of creating a second independent apartment, perfect for use as a bed and breakfast, guest house or holiday home. Quiet setting, a few minutes from the main services, ideal for those looking for a spacious solution, immersed in tranquility, with residential and receptive potential.', 'Pareto', 'Alessandria', 'piemonte', 'via Montegrappa', 44.5147696, 8.4515801, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33368338/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d9/58/69/715305666.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d9/58/69/715305666.webp"]', 57, 'villa', 'villa', 60.0, 76.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 54.0, 72.0, 815.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 33.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (140, '34373533', 319000.0, 100.0, 3, 2, 'Detached house in via Brancasi no number', 'Small Palace with Private Pool, Jacuzzi and Sea View – Ostuni Historic Center In an exclusive location just a few steps from the historic center of Ostuni, an elegant small palace with air-conditioned accommodation, private pool and panoramic terrace with Jacuzzi and spectacular views of the sea and the White City. A property with attention to detail, characterized by a Mediterranean style that recalls the atmospheres between Puglia and Greece. Main features 2 uniquely designed bedrooms: One bedroom with private whirlpool tub One bedroom with bathroom carved into the stone, authentic and evocative 2 complete and modern bathrooms Bright dining area Kitchen equipped with complete utensils and equipment Panoramic balcony with sea and mountain views Terrace with large Jacuzzi and breathtaking views of the historic center and the sea External features Private pool for exclusive use Livable outdoor spaces, perfect for moments of relaxation Open view of the countryside, the sea and the profiles of the historic center Comfort Air conditioning in all rooms Elegant Mediterranean style, with references to Apulian architecture and the Greek islands Modern, functional and refined environments with quality materials An exclusive solution in the heart of the White City, ideal for those looking for charm, comfort and spectacular views in an authentic and atmospheric context. Points of interest: The Municipality of Ostuni is part of the province of Brindisi and is located in the Altosalento area, about 7 km from the sea, 30 km from Brindisi airport. Also called White City for its characteristic historic center painted with white lime. Its territory is an integral part of the Itria Valley and the Southern Murgia. A renowned tourist center, from 2008 to today it has always received the Blue Flag for its coast with beautiful beaches and crystal clear waters, and is among the most loved destinations by tourists who cannot fail to admire and appreciate its beauties. The city, which has p', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'via Brancasi no number', 40.7344637, 17.5776544, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34373533/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/cb/ae/34/758514481.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/cb/ae/34/758514481.webp"]', 38, 'independantHouse', 'house', 59.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 63.0, 85.0, 3190.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 82.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (141, '34770076', 2000000.0, 300.0, 12, 10, 'Villa in strada Provinciale 16 no number', 'Exclusive accommodation facility in the Ostuni hills – Restored trulli, swimming pool, and wellness services In the heart of the Itria Valley, nestled in the charming hills of Ostuni, we offer for sale a prestigious accommodation facility comprising finely restored ancient trulli and a recently redeveloped main area. An oasis of charm, ideal for those wishing to invest in a high-level tourist complex, perfectly integrated into the Apulian landscape. The Property The facility offers a unique combination of authenticity, modern comforts, and dedicated wellness services: Two Dream Suites created in masterfully restored trulli, with furnishings that respect the original materials and architecture. Six rooms with private bathrooms, located in the main part of the facility. Three double rooms within the trulli. Many accommodations feature a private patio, air conditioning, WiFi, and some include a whirlpool tub, satellite TV, and a kitchenette. Services and Comforts Panoramic swimming pool immersed in the natural surroundings of the hills. Outdoor whirlpool tub. Large, perfectly manicured terrace and garden. Multipurpose sports court (basketball, volleyball, football). Charging station for electric vehicles. Location Situated in a privileged and highly sought-after area of Ostuni, the property is located: A few minutes from the Adriatic Sea, Not far from the Ionian Sea, Close to the Torre Guaceto Nature Reserve, In a strategic position to reach art cities like Taranto and its points of interest (Cathedral, Aragonese Castle). Why Choose It This facility represents a unique opportunity for those who wish to: Invest in the high-end tourism sector, Manage an already established and charming hospitality business, Acquire a typical complex of the Itria Valley with high potential. Land Description: The land is approximately 10,000 sqm and is on a flat position. Points of Interest: Ostuni, one of the jewels of Alto Salento in the province of Brindisi, is about 7 km from the beach', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'strada Provinciale 16 no number', 40.7005917, 17.4915172, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34770076/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/29/44/c0/768444016.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/29/44/c0/768444016.webp"]', 45, 'villa', 'torre', 59.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 74.0, 80.0, 6667.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 78.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (142, '33787567', 750000.0, 130.0, 10, 4, 'Villa in contrada Salinola no number', 'VILLA AUREA OSTUNI – SARACEN TRULLO WITH POOL AMONG THE OLIVE GROVES Key Features: -Saracen trullo with extension – approx. 130 sqm -Fenced plot of 1 hectare with olive trees and fruit orchard -Private pool with sunbathing area -4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, fully equipped kitchen -Double veranda, outdoor kitchen with pergola -Radiator heating + hot/cold heat pump system -Private artesian well, gated access -High rental potential and strategic location in the Valle d’Itria Bathed in the warm light of the Valle d’Itria, just 4 km from the White City of Ostuni and about 10 km from the crystal-clear waters of the Adriatic Sea, Villa Aurea is a timeless retreat where the beauty of ancient stone meets the comforts of modern living. This exclusive property — with its authentic and sophisticated soul — extends over approximately one hectare of Apulian countryside, carefully landscaped with century-old olive trees and fruit plants. The land is fully fenced, ensuring privacy, tranquillity, and security. At the heart of the estate lies an elegant Saracen trullo, beautifully restored and extended to create a living space of approx. 130 sqm, designed to embrace outdoor living and the joy of hospitality. The living area opens into a Mediterranean-style kitchen, ideal for lively dinners with friends or long, sun-drenched breakfasts. The night area features four bedrooms, each with its own private en-suite bathroom, offering both comfort and privacy — perfect for a private residence or a boutique hospitality project. Outside, two large covered verandas and an outdoor kitchen beneath a pergola create fluid transitions between inside and outside, ideal for enjoying the Apulian climate in all seasons. The private swimming pool is discreetly nestled among the traditional stone walls and the silvery green of the olive trees, creating picture-perfect views and moments of absolute relaxation. The villa is equipped with radiator heating, air conditioning (hot/cold) via heat pumps, and an indep', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'contrada Salinola no number', 40.7065137, 17.5883736, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33787567/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/83/b6/59/750733427.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/83/b6/59/750733427.webp"]', 64, 'villa', 'trullo', 59.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 66.0, 84.0, 5769.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 85.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (143, '25641189', 750000.0, 150.0, 8, 3, 'Trullo in contrada Tamburroni no number', 'TRULLO MANGO MAIN DETAILS  •Luxury trullo with pool  •In the countryside of Ostuni •Interior surface of about 150sqm •Land area of about 6,000sqm  •Three bedrooms and three bathrooms •Spa area with Jacuzzi LUXURY TRULLO WITH SWIMMING POOL AND JACUZZI IN OSTUNI, UPPER SALENTO, APULIA Rising proudly among the whispering olive groves that surround it, Trullo Mango is a dwelling in perfect Itria Valley style. Today, the trullo is an oasis of Apulian tranquillity, with carefully preserved original features, an abundance of space, contemporary comforts and a stunning swimming pool, all just a couple of kilometres from beautiful Ostuni and the Adriatic Sea.  DETAILED DESCRIPTION OF THE TRULLO THE INTERIOR: Trullo Mango is spread over a single level, inside it accommodates three comfortable bedrooms, all with en-suite bathrooms, one in the double trullo and the other two are divided into a double and a twin with single beds. The spaces are characterised by stone barrel vaults: large covered veranda, living room with fully equipped open kitchen. A corridor leads to the sleeping area. The property is completed by a small spa with Jacuzzi and private sitting room. OUTSIDE: Outside, there are numerous finely furnished spaces that allow you to enjoy life in the open air, including the large porch facing the pool, complete with dining area and outdoor living. Also enchanting is the overflow swimming pool with chlorine system, measuring 10x4m and with a constant depth of 1.40m, strictly in stone with two gazebos, barbecue and wood-burning oven. The garden covers about 6,000 square metres, wonderfully planted with olive trees and Mediterranean shrubs.  FACILITIES: Trullo Mango has double glazed windows, mosquito nets, alarm system.', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'contrada Tamburroni no number', 40.7308238, 17.6381926, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/25641189/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/4b/03/b3/749884753.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/4b/03/b3/749884753.webp"]', 83, 'trullo', 'trullo', 59.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 69.0, 84.0, 5000.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 87.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (144, '34512234', 1150000.0, 600.0, 10, 6, 'Estate in strada Provinciale Alberese, 59', 'Immersed in the greenery of the Maremma Natural Park, at the foot of the Uccellina mountains, a prestigious agricultural estate with accommodation business is for sale. The property is located in one of the most fascinating and protected areas of Tuscany, known throughout the world for its natural beauty. The complex consists of an old stone farmhouse of approximately 500 square meters, located on 1.5 hectares of flat land, within which there are approximately IGP olive trees in full production, a small orchard and a vineyard. Agricultural outbuildings for approximately 3,500 cubic meters complete the property. The main building has undergone a major renovation; only the large living room on the ground floor needs some finishing touches. The garden/park has also been completely renovated, starting from the entrance, embellished with an important wrought iron gate with stone sides and rows of cypresses leading to the residence. Next to the main farmhouse there is an independent building of approximately 60 square meters, ideal as a further housing unit, outbuilding or accommodation for guests or staff. The property enjoys an absolutely privileged position: within the Maremma Natural Park it is rare to find such a large, versatile and well-structured agricultural estate. The particularly favorable microclimate allows the start of different types of crops. The plains of Alberese, a hamlet of the Municipality of Grosseto where the property is located, are renowned for the fertility of the land and ease of cultivation. In addition to agricultural activity, the area offers excellent accommodation opportunities, with a good tourist influx even during the winter season, thanks to the mild climate and the natural and cultural richness of the area. The location is strategic: the beaches of Marina di Alberese, Talamone and the Costa d''Argento (Monte Argentario) can be reached in a short time, as well as the locations on the north coast such as Principina a Mare, Marina di Gros', 'Grosseto', 'Grosseto', 'toscana', 'strada Provinciale Alberese, 59', 42.6485825, 11.1272569, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34512234/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/7b/c5/cf/758517438.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/7b/c5/cf/758517438.webp"]', 56, 'countryHouse', 'farmhouse', 59.0, 63.0, 40.0, 40.0, 64.0, 58.0, 69.0, 1917.0, 'Firenze (FLR)', 129.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (145, '33296834', 640000.0, 316.0, 5, 3, 'Villa in località Ghirlanda no number', 'MASSA MARITTIMA (GR): Villa with swimming pool a few minutes from Massa Marittima The context Villa with garden, cypress avenue and swimming pool two minutes from the historic center of Massa Marittima. The interior is spread over three floors and is in excellent condition. The exterior is kept in an exemplary manner with local and exotic plants, fruit trees, plus covered and uncovered terraces, a barbecue area and a view of Massa Marittima. The location is perfect because the farmhouse is easily accessible and is in a quiet and very peaceful area. Short description Ground floor: living room, large living room with equipped kitchenette and a fully glazed room. First floor: two bedrooms and a bathroom with shower. First basement: two bathrooms and 5 large rooms. Utilities The property is connected to the city''s gas, water and electricity networks. Infrastructure and services Massa Marittima has absolutely all essential services. Pisa Airport: 128Km Sea (Follonica): 18Km 316 sq m IMPORTANT: READ THE NOTE ON INFORMATION PUBLISHED BY CASE DI FAMIGLIA.', 'Massa Marittima', 'Grosseto', 'toscana', 'località Ghirlanda no number', 43.0563678, 10.901957, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33296834/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/df/95/4f/713024176.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/df/95/4f/713024176.webp"]', 38, 'villa', 'farmhouse', 59.0, 58.0, 40.0, 60.0, 64.0, 62.0, 62.0, 2025.0, 'Pisa (PSA)', 81.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (146, '32527987', 480000.0, 180.0, 10, 3, 'Village house in loc.Orbicciano 44, 44', 'A refuge in a characteristic hilltop village in the direction of the sea, a charming stone rustic house in the hills of Camaiore. Here time seems to have stood still, the rhythms are slow, the silence makes us relax. The rustic house, renovated about 15 years ago, has an incredible charm, especially for the authenticity of the materials and the structure; every detail has been thought out and studied directly by the owner, as this is his family home. The house has 3 entrances, two on the ground floor and one on the first floor. Through a characteristic alleyway, we reach the first entrance on the ground floor, where a hallway leads us to a dining area equipped with a built-in barbecue, a wood-fired oven, and a beautiful stone sink; and to the stairs for access to the first floor. The external entrance on the first floor is via a beautiful original serpentine marble staircase, from here you access the living-dining room with a fireplace, kitchen, and bathroom. Going up to the first floor, we find the bedrooms, a wardrobe area, and the bathroom. Adjacent, we find the other two-story building where the ground floor is used as a wine cellar, and a laundry/technical room, the first floor is a single room currently used as a billiard room, and a bathroom serving the swimming pool, which is located in the small garden with a view of the hills, as well as terraced land of about 600 sqm. Authenticity, tranquility, and view.', 'Camaiore', 'Lucca', 'toscana', 'loc.Orbicciano 44, 44', 43.9111314, 10.3929564, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32527987/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/c5/1d/b0/686768041.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/c5/1d/b0/686768041.webp"]', 35, 'casaDePueblo', 'villa', 59.0, 29.0, 40.0, 100.0, 64.0, 68.0, 71.0, 2667.0, 'Pisa (PSA)', 25.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (147, '35042571', 500000.0, 195.0, 7, 2, 'Villa in via Ulivi, 241', 'Why buy it? *3,000 m² of property, 195 m² the house, 30 m² the outbuilding, 72 m² the swimming pool *Refurbished and furnished, heating and cooling with solar panel system * Privacy and tranquility a stone''s throw from everything, from the sea, from the hills and from the city   The property: the villa is located within a nature reserve, it covers an area of 3,000 m² inside which we find a beautiful, well-kept park with plants and flowers, the house on two levels, the large swimming pool and an outbuilding.   The house has been renovated and equipped with solar panel systems for heating and cooling, the living area develops on the ground floor with the entrance into a large living room, separated by a wall with three arches an open equipped and well organized kitchen adorned with a splendid fireplace, and a bathroom. The solid wood staircase leads up to the upper floor where there is a second bathroom and three bedrooms, the master bedroom with walk-in closet. The patio with outdoor sitting area accompanies the exit to the pool. At the end of the park there is an annex for guests with living / sleeping area, kitchen and bathroom. The entire perimeter of the area is controlled by a remotely monitored alarm system.   The area and connections: the villa is well connected to the via Lucchese Romana, it can be reached in 5 minutes by car from the Altopascio-Autostrada A11 exit. It is located 20 km from Lucca, 40 km from Pisa, 50 km from Viareggio and 70 km from Florence.   housestobuy. it |.', 'Castelfranco di Sotto', 'Pisa', 'toscana', 'via Ulivi, 241', 43.7976, 10.6921938, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/35042571/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/9d/0d/e4/778510102.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/9d/0d/e4/778510102.webp"]', 60, 'villa', 'villa', 59.0, 33.0, 40.0, 100.0, 64.0, 63.0, 71.0, 2564.0, 'Pisa (PSA)', 27.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (148, '27858640', 8000000.0, 1300.0, 9, 11, 'Villa', 'This prestigious estate for sale near Florence is of extraordinary historical and artistic interest, has 3 levels and measures 1,300 sqm. It features a private chapel, ancient underground thermal baths, a spa area and a convenient lift. On the facades, there are a loggia, balconies, terraces and panoramic porticoes with a view of Florence and the property''s majestic 2000-sqm Italian garden, embellished with fountains and statues and surrounded by an 8,000-sqm olive grove for a total external surface of 1 hectare. This historical villa dates back to the 14th century, although it took on its present form in the Renaissance. Frequented by the Medici family for recreation, over the centuries this prestigious estate has continued to welcome historical and illustrious figures. From the large frescoed entrance, we enter the annex on the left, while on the right there is a big kitchen with access to the garden and rooms. Continuing along the corridor we reach the incredible main hall, with a very high vaulted ceiling and a big fireplace, and a refined dining room. There is then a study and other rooms that will enchant you with their timeless beauty. The best jewel set in this majestic historical villa is the family chapel with a vaulted ceiling. The area is completed by a winter garden and a spacious independent study with its own bathroom and kitchenette. Upstairs is the sleeping area: 5 en-suite bedrooms, including a master bedroom with a huge wardrobe. There is also an independent apartment for guests. This majestic villa is a real dream home, with its tidy garden, its perfectly preserved features and modern comforts. Ref: 10046.', 'Firenze', 'Firenze', 'toscana', 'Neighbourhood: Serpiolle - Massoni', 43.8228692, 11.2457213, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/27858640/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/8b/77/83/662665661.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/8b/77/83/662665661.webp"]', 20, 'villa', 'villa', 59.0, 0.0, 40.0, 100.0, 95.0, 57.0, 74.0, 6154.0, 'Firenze (FLR)', 4.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (149, '34009352', 950000.0, 400.0, 15, 4, 'Estate in via Campoli', 'San Casciano Prima periferia beautiful completely independent farmhouse located in the Chianti countryside, but not isolated a stone''s throw from all the most important wineries, the property is in good condition but requires a light renovation while the barn is completely to be renovated. The property is divided into two units: THE FIRST UNIT Used for hospitality purposes, the property is composed of two residential units: the first consists of an entrance hall, kitchen, living room, two large bathrooms, a small utility room, on the upper floor there is a hallway, three large bedrooms, a bathroom. The second unit is composed of a large kitchen with fireplace, a very bright living room, on the upper floor there is a hallway, a double bedroom, a double bedroom, a bathroom, a wardrobe. As an appendix to the property, there is a greenhouse that can be used by renovating it as an extension of the house. BARN Opposite the farmhouse, it is in need of renovation and has two large rooms on the ground floor and a very large and bright room on the first floor. The property includes approximately 4000 m2 of land. DISTANCES TO CITIES OF ART Florence 25km Arezzo 85km Siena 60km Peretola Airport 40 km Chianti 0 km.', 'San Casciano in Val di Pesa', 'Firenze', 'toscana', 'via Campoli', 43.6229073, 11.2469532, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34009352/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/cf/b7/e6/738065928.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/cf/b7/e6/738065928.webp"]', 67, 'countryHouse', 'farmhouse', 59.0, 42.0, 40.0, 100.0, 64.0, 57.0, 65.0, 2375.0, 'Firenze (FLR)', 21.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (150, '35116790', 135000.0, 184.0, 4, 2, 'Detached house in vicolo Ricovero, 12', 'ORISTANO - VIA RICOVERO We offer for sale a detached house with a double entrance on two levels with a large terrace. The property is internally composed of a first entrance from Via Ricovero with access to the living room with a wood-burning fireplace and a private kitchenette. Through the hallway, you access the dining room and the bathroom with a window and bathtub overlooking the service shaft. From the same hallway, we find the second entrance from Vico Ricovero and the staircase leading to the first floor, where we have access to the hallway that leads to each room. The first room we access is the exit to the furnished terrace overlooking Via Ricovero, the double bedroom, the single bedroom, and the bathroom with a window and shower.', 'Oristano', 'Oristano', 'sardegna', 'vicolo Ricovero, 12', 39.90668, 8.5985378, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/35116790/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/95/3b/41/780720701.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/95/3b/41/780720701.webp"]', 20, 'independantHouse', 'house', 59.0, 100.0, 40.0, 60.0, 56.0, 41.0, 50.0, 734.0, 'Cagliari (CAG)', 83.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (151, '33466413', 295000.0, 260.0, 5, 2, 'Detached house in piazza Fontana', 'In Trecasali there is a house that doesn''t come on the market every day. An independent home, ready to welcome those who desire ample space, comfort, and the freedom of a double entrance that multiplies the possibilities of use. On the first floor, you are greeted by a bright entrance with a terrace, a living room ideal for moments of conviviality, a separate kitchen perfect for those who love to cook without compromise, three bedrooms, and a bathroom with a bathtub that preserves the flavor of a family home. The ground floor, connected internally but with independent access, adds value: two rooms plus a bathroom that become a small apartment for guests, parents, or adult children seeking autonomy. The double garage completes the property, giving breath and practicality to daily life. Anyone who knows Trecasali knows how rare it is to find independent houses with this flexibility and size: similar properties are quickly absorbed by the market, especially by those looking for a two-family or investment solution. Don''t miss the opportunity to make your own a space that can adapt to the different phases of life. Contact us today via WhatsApp with the code PARMA716 to book a visit: the right house doesn''t wait.', 'Sissa Trecasali', 'Parma', 'emilia-romagna', 'piazza Fontana', 44.9382021, 10.2694423, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33466413/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a7/93/91/741721377.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a7/93/91/741721377.webp"]', 97, 'independantHouse', 'house', 59.0, 79.0, 40.0, 60.0, 56.0, 43.0, 65.0, 1135.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 92.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (152, '35123668', 149000.0, 145.0, 4, 1, 'Terraced house in via Roma, 30', 'End-terrace house with a private garden on three sides. We offer for sale an end-terrace house, free on three sides, characterized by ample spaces and great potential, ideal for families seeking independence and convenience. The property is arranged over multiple levels and is surrounded by a private garden on three sides, perfect for outdoor moments, a relaxation area, or for those who desire an exclusive green space. The internal layout is as follows: Ground floor: living area with living room and kitchen First floor: two bedrooms and bathroom Second floor: two bedrooms and a closet Top floor: unfinished attic, with the possibility of customization. The house offers spacious and well-distributed rooms, with many possibilities for adaptation to one''s needs. Available and free immediately. Excellent solution for those seeking independence, space, and a private garden.', 'Carpi', 'Modena', 'emilia-romagna', 'via Roma, 30', 44.8140129, 10.8406594, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/35123668/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/6e/94/ac/780957430.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/6e/94/ac/780957430.webp"]', 25, 'terracedHouse', 'house', 59.0, 86.0, 40.0, 80.0, 56.0, 45.0, 51.0, 1028.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 47.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (153, '29814685', 100000.0, 164.0, 8, 1, 'Detached house in località Garbarini, 17', 'Farm estate in an exceptional location ready to be restarted. The main house of 164 sqm has a completely renovated structure with the restoration of a traditional stone house. Provision for heating with a fireplace and ducted hot air. The accessory spaces of warehouses and stables are approximately 250 sqm and the available land is 4150 sqm directly surrounding it, but with adjacent plots it can reach approximately 20 hectares. The setting is that of the green Garbarini basin, 5 minutes by car from the services of Mioglia and 30 minutes from the sea of Albisola. This typical peasant hamlet is the right place to achieve a lifestyle of yesteryear. Charming.', 'Pareto', 'Alessandria', 'piemonte', 'località Garbarini, 17', 44.5048893, 8.4432698, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/29814685/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f1/3a/0a/616168411.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f1/3a/0a/616168411.webp"]', 28, 'independantHouse', 'house', 59.0, 95.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 47.0, 54.0, 610.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 33.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (154, '31263502', 120000.0, 160.0, 6, 1, 'Detached house in Sp334, 39', 'Ancient stone farmhouse set in a typical village and completely renovated, 600 sqm garden with a well, developed on two levels: on the ground floor a large garage, tavern with wood-burning oven, cellars, boiler room, on the first floor entrance to a living room, large loggia and splendid kitchen, two bedrooms, walk-in closet. (new and certified electrical, plumbing and heating systems, alarm, video surveillance). Its convenience to the road, to Cartosio and to Acqui Terme, also make it ideal as a first home. To visit!', 'Malvicino', 'Alessandria', 'piemonte', 'SP334, 39', 44.5589764, 8.432568, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/31263502/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d1/32/0f/647996020.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d1/32/0f/647996020.webp"]', 30, 'independantHouse', 'farmhouse', 59.0, 82.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 59.0, 57.0, 750.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 36.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (155, '22039692', 2200000.0, 720.0, 19, 10, 'Masseria in via rialbo no number', 'DESCRIPTION Masseria of about 400 square meters + crusher of 200 square meters and two farmhouses in the surrounding land of 50 and 60 square meters. Land of 21 hectares of centuries-old olive grove, between Ostuni and Montalbano. FEATURES O Wood oven O Garden O Sea view O Piazzale O Parking space O Autonomous O Balcony / s O Terrace O Fireplace.', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'via rialbo no number', 40.7580965, 17.5285216, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/22039692/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/70/86/a2/758633425.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/70/86/a2/758633425.webp"]', 69, 'masseria', 'masseria', 58.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 67.0, 81.0, 3056.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 77.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (156, '32468779', 850000.0, 122.0, 6, 4, 'Villa in contrada Piatone no number', 'Panoramic villa with pool and luxury finishes in Ostuni – In a privileged position with breathtaking panoramic views, we offer for sale a prestigious independent villa immersed in the quiet countryside, with an infinity pool and large private land. Interiors – Elegance and comfort in every room The house is spread over one level with large and well-distributed spaces. The entrance opens onto a bright open space, embellished with barrel vaults that recall the traditional local architecture, with a living area and a finely furnished open-plan kitchen. The sleeping area includes three bedrooms and four bathrooms, all made with high-quality materials and equipped with every comfort. The villa is equipped with underfloor heating and air conditioning in all rooms, guaranteeing energy efficiency and maximum well-being throughout the year. Triple-glazed windows, Starlink internet connection, advanced home automation (management of gate, external lighting, air conditioning and heating), complete the picture of the latest generation internal equipment. Exterior – Relaxation and privacy in nature The outdoor area is a true oasis of relaxation, with a spectacular 40 sq m infinity pool, surrounded by an equipped solarium area. A large covered veranda houses comfortable sitting areas to enjoy the tranquility of the place, while a complete equipped outdoor kitchen allows you to fully enjoy the summer in company. A jacuzzi hot tub overlooking the surrounding landscape makes this property unique. The land, measuring 10,280 sq m, is completely fenced with a dry stone wall, respecting the local aesthetics and privacy. Technical features and pluses of the property Advanced home automation for remote management of main functions High-efficiency triple-glazed windows Underfloor heating and air conditioning system in every room High-performance internet system (Starlink type) Dry stone wall fencing for security and privacy Cistern and Imhoff tank Provision for photovoltaic panels Surveill', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'contrada Piatone no number', 40.664578, 17.5801828, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32468779/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/58/f7/84/685351518.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/58/f7/84/685351518.webp"]', 64, 'villa', 'villa', 58.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 65.0, 83.0, 6967.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 87.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (157, '35123329', 80000.0, 133.0, 3, 1, 'Detached house in via Poerio Carlo, 22', 'In the heart of the municipality of Sava, we offer for sale a 133 sqm independent house, ideal for those who wish to personalize their home. The property, to be renovated, offers ample spaces that lend themselves to various housing solutions, allowing for the creation of tailor-made environments for one''s needs. Natural light characterizes every corner of the house, making the interior spaces cozy and livable. The central location guarantees easy access to the services and amenities of the town, while the independence of the property ensures privacy and tranquility. This property represents a unique opportunity for those seeking a home to transform according to their own taste, in an area rich in tradition and culture.', 'Sava', 'Taranto', 'puglia', 'via Poerio Carlo, 22', 40.4034072, 17.5542884, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/35123329/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/b2/e1/1d/780950986.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/b2/e1/1d/780950986.webp"]', 23, 'independantHouse', 'house', 58.0, 100.0, 40.0, 40.0, 60.0, 39.0, 48.0, 602.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 106.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (158, '33127866', 108000.0, 139.0, 7, 2, 'Terraced house in via Schirra no number', 'Judicial Auction - A.P.I. Srl Reference 235.2023.120526 TARANTO This is a Judicial Sale with the Assistance of A.P.I. Srl, a reference firm for acquisitions of properties in Judicial Auctions and pre-auction purchases. Address the real estate enforcement market, following the correct legal protocol. ____________________________________________________ LOCATION Via Schirra snc – CASTELLANETA (TA) Terraced house consisting of a basement, raised ground floor, and first floor with an adjoining garden on two sides for exclusive use and with independent access from Via Schirra. ____________________________________________________ INSURANCE POLICY "The property is insurable in Judicial Auctions" - Buy by insuring your property, ask for a quote for an insurance policy against theft and damage from the best companies in contact with our firm, who will be able to provide the best solutions. ____________________________________________________ ASTE PREASTE INVESTIMENTI srl We operate with our clients in a totally personalized way. Our professionals are regularly registered and licensed to practice their profession, not mere collaborators, but Authorized Agents and Proxies who can accompany you and allow you to achieve the goals you have set for yourselves. They will be with you from the initial stages until the handover of the property and will be your point of contact for any aspect related to the purchase and management of the asset. Strength, Courtesy, Professionalism, Experience, Solidity, Transparency are just some of our characteristics, and we are certain that we can make a difference in the real estate auction market, as we represent "determination and security" to achieve the goals of our clients. ____________________________________________________ ASTE PREASTE INVESTIMENTI Srl We operate based on criteria and guidelines strongly focused on the analysis and constant verification of the structure and related organizational processes, always operating with a critical a', 'Castellaneta', 'Taranto', 'puglia', 'via Schirra no number', 40.4772778, 16.9388825, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33127866/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/e7/34/3c/780022371.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/e7/34/3c/780022371.webp"]', 35, 'terracedHouse', 'house', 58.0, 85.0, 40.0, 60.0, 60.0, 45.0, 51.0, 777.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 75.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (159, '34860745', 180000.0, 67.0, 3, 1, 'Detached house in via Pineta, 70', 'This property stands out for its extraordinary open view: from the surrounding olive groves to the rolling green hills, all the way to the shimmering sea facing Albenga. The portico and the private courtyard offer a privileged vantage point, creating a sense of space, tranquillity and Mediterranean atmosphere. The house is free on all four sides and offers **67 sqm of commercial surface**. It was completely rebuilt in **2001** using traditional masonry, replacing the previous prefabricated structure. It is in excellent condition and is sold **fully furnished**, ready to move into. The interior layout is functional and welcoming: spacious living area with open-plan kitchen, hallway, double bedroom, single bedroom and a bathroom with window and shower. Technical features include **independent methane heating**, **air conditioning** with two units in the bedrooms, and **PVC windows** with double glazing and mosquito screens. The **attic**, accessible via a retractable ladder, is **walkable** and ideal for storage. Outdoors, the **private courtyard surrounding the house on all four sides** ensures privacy and comfort. In addition to the panoramic portico, the courtyard includes a **separate utility room** with **sink and laundry area**. Access to the Versolmar Residence is regulated by a **year‑round concierge service**; when the concierge is off duty, entry is controlled by an **automatic gate** that residents can open via remote control, magnetic card or remotely. Annual condominium fees amount to approximately **€900**, including water consumption. Distances to main points of interest:  - **Albenga beaches: approx. 10–12 minutes by car**  - **Alassio: approx. 20 minutes**  - **Cisano sul Neva: a few minutes**  - **A10 motorway (Albenga exit): approx. 10 minutes**  - **Genoa Airport: approx. 1 hour**  - **Hiking trails, medieval villages and essential services: easily reachable** A perfect solution for those seeking independence, peaceful surroundings, a stunning view', 'Cisano sul Neva', 'Savona', 'liguria', 'via Pineta, 70', 44.0783501, 8.1315021, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34860745/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a9/f1/b8/771682031.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a9/f1/b8/771682031.webp"]', 34, 'independantHouse', 'villa', 58.0, 54.0, 40.0, 60.0, 60.0, 47.0, 74.0, 2687.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 67.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (160, '32454201', 530000.0, 430.0, 15, 9, 'Detached house in località Columabargia', '**Agritourism and accomodation facility for sale in the wonderful Sardinia** Discover this pretty property located on the splendid Central-Western coast of Sardinia, at just 15 minutes to Bosa and 5 minutes to Tresnuraghes. Plunged in an agricultural area of inestimable beauty, this property offers a large plot of approximately seven hectares, surrounded by rich Mediterranean bushes in an enchanting and relaxing atmosphere, with scents and colours that draw a landscape to admire for hours, in its seasonal changes, at dawn or at sunset, a few minutes to Punta Foghe and the beautiful and still wild beach of Columbargia. In this context, immersed in the lush, green and silent countryside, the property is perfect for those who love nature and tranquillity. Recently used as an agritourism and accomodation facility, the building has numerous well-lit and large spaces, perfect to welcome guests. With 8 bedrooms and 6 bathrooms, it is ideal for those who want to start an accomodation business or for a family looking for a spacious and comfortable residence. The kitchen is fully equipped to meet the needs of an agritourism business, while the outdoor spaces include a storage, an oven and a barbeque, and a covered veranda of over 50 square meters, perfect to enjoy beautiful days outdoors. The property also has a large swimming pool (14 X 7) and a well with water reserve, ensuring comfort and sustainability. The buildings are in good condition, although they are in need of maintenance and updating works to fully exploit their potential. In addition, there is the possibility to change the use, subject to permission. The property is also suitable for people with reduced mobility. Don''t miss the opportunity to own a corner of Paradise in Sardinia, where natural beauty meets modern comfort. Contact us for more information and to book a viewing!', 'Tresnuraghes', 'Oristano', 'sardegna', 'località Columabargia', 40.2529329, 8.520197, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32454201/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/3d/a3/b6/684755676.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/3d/a3/b6/684755676.webp"]', 38, 'independantHouse', 'house', 58.0, 82.0, 40.0, 40.0, 56.0, 47.0, 61.0, 1233.0, 'Olbia (OLB)', 111.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (161, '33983554', 390000.0, 226.0, 5, 1, 'Detached house in via Orelia no number', 'Grizzana Morandi (Alto Appennino Bolognese) Do you know the high hills of Bologna? I''m referring to those that embrace Porretta, or rather, a little before... between Vergato and Riola. Here, in this stretch of the Apennines, the landscape changes tone: it''s not yet a real mountain, but not a plain either. They are high hills, almost suspended, that look like green waves at altitude. Wheat, hay, oak and chestnut woods alternate with elegance. And in the midst of all this nature, historical villages, artistic monuments, and natural wonders emerge. Do you want to know which ones? I''ll tell you at the end. This is one of those areas that, over time, will become increasingly sought after. An investment for the future: good air, altitude, coolness even in summer. And it''s not at all isolated: there are two train stops and a main road that takes you to Bologna in less than an hour. And it is from this road that my story begins. I turn right and take a small road that follows the profile of the hills, going up and down gently. Here and there, some houses in the countryside, some villages with stone houses, all carefully renovated. You can see that there is love for the territory here. Everything is tidy, everything is respected. After a few kilometers I arrive at Oreglia di Sotto, an ancient village often mentioned in local guides as one of the most beautiful in the area. And I confirm it: it is truly enchanting. The house I want to show you today is located right here. Giulia, the owner, is waiting for me. She has already arranged everything for the visit. I park my Panda in the private space, outside the fence. I enter the first garden: a stone table dominates a teak platform, with lights set in for evening lighting. It is the "living room" garden. Three steps separate the teak area from the green area, with a manicured lawn, three historic olive trees and a majestic cork oak. I had never seen one: it is imposing, fascinating, almost magnetic. Giulia''s house dates back t', 'Grizzana Morandi', 'Bologna', 'emilia-romagna', 'via Orelia no number', 44.2297194, 11.0995505, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33983554/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d6/d9/65/737258181.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d6/d9/65/737258181.webp"]', 107, 'independantHouse', 'villa', 58.0, 42.0, 40.0, 80.0, 56.0, 61.0, 73.0, 1726.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 37.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (162, '33672218', 395000.0, 275.0, 7, 3, 'Villa in via di Sant Andrea no number', 'For info: 335/5243208 - Sant''Andrea, villa on a plot of 1,280 m², developed on two levels of 130 m² each, composed of: Ground floor, entrance hall, 43 m² living room, 23 m² kitchen, study, bathroom, closet and large terrace; First floor, 4 bedrooms, walk-in closet, 2 bathrooms, terrace and balcony: The property includes a 1,100 m² park and a double-width garage. Please note that the published address may not correspond to the exact location of the property in order to protect the privacy of the seller - Reference: 024/EB For information: Mediatori Associati Parma srl - Tel. 335/5243208 or 0521/281131 WE ARE AVAILABLE FOR A FREE EVALUATION OF YOUR PROPERTY!', 'Torrile', 'Parma', 'emilia-romagna', 'via di Sant Andrea no number', 44.9011808, 10.3310677, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33672218/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/79/79/bb/734530626.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/79/79/bb/734530626.webp"]', 34, 'villa', 'villa', 58.0, 60.0, 40.0, 60.0, 56.0, 51.0, 70.0, 1436.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 86.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (163, '30221680', 450000.0, 250.0, 9, 4, 'Terraced house in via Pietro Giardini, 567', 'REF. 485 - Villa in SAN FAUSTINO - internal VIALE AMENDOLA. We offer for sale a villa in a quiet area, inside Viale Amendola, with independent entrance and fenced garden of approximately 150 square meters plus private parking spaces, double garage and laundry room. The property is in good condition and offers large and bright spaces distributed over 9 rooms. On the ground floor: - entrance, - double garage - study. On the 2nd floor: - corridor - living room - dining room - kitchenette - sleeping area that houses 3 good-sized bedrooms - 2 bathrooms - 2 balconies. On the upper floor: - further large living room - kitchen - bedroom - bathroom, which can be used as a further living area or as a professional studio. Excellent also as a parent-child solution. Do not hesitate to contact us for further information or to book a visit IMMOBILIARE DEL CORSO, Corso Cavour 62 Modena.', 'Modena', 'Modena', 'emilia-romagna', 'via Pietro Giardini, 567', 44.6351219, 10.9042056, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/30221680/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/1d/31/72/693433409.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/1d/31/72/693433409.webp"]', 68, 'terracedHouse', 'villa', 58.0, 38.0, 40.0, 80.0, 75.0, 54.0, 66.0, 1800.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 32.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (164, '34974621', 263000.0, 271.0, 10, 3, 'Detached house in Regione San Rocco', 'Piedmontese farmhouse with garden and panoramic views! In a hillside postion, with a quiet and secluded setting, this Piedmontese farmhouse retains the authentic character of traditional architecture, offering well-proportioned and easy-living spaces. On the ground floor we find the main rooms of the house: living room, kitchen, small bathroom, bedroom and the large, bright and convivial lounge overlooking the garden. The main entrance leads to a staircase that takes you to the upper floors. On the first floor, there are three good-sized bedrooms served by two bathrooms. The floor is completed by the former hayloft, which houses an airy loft with large windows, a solution that adds character and movement to the rooms without weighing them down. In the basement, there is a classic brick-vaulted cellar. Outside, the private garden is fully usable, offering private spaces that are easy to maintain. A balanced and versatile property, suitable both as a main residence and as a second home, ideal for those who want to enjoy the countryside with naturalness, comfort and privacy.', 'Agliano Terme', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'Regione San Rocco', 44.7975424, 8.2457182, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34974621/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a0/71/5f/776230069.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a0/71/5f/776230069.webp"]', 89, 'independantHouse', 'farmhouse', 58.0, 62.0, 15.0, 60.0, 54.0, 63.0, 73.0, 970.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 63.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (165, '33716983', 690000.0, 800.0, 16, 8, 'Casale/cascina in strada Vai, 7', '*Renovated farmhouse already used as a farmhouse with 14,000 square meters of private land* In Cocconato, in the Borgata Bonvino, in a hilly position, surrounded by greenery and the tranquility of the countryside, we offer for sale a charming, completely renovated farmhouse, already used as a farmhouse. The property extends over approximately 14,000 square meters of private land, ideal for those who wish to live in contact with nature or start a hospitality business, and the main building is currently divided into: -2 independent apartments, perfect for both private use and hospitality; -outbuilding with the possibility of creating up to 4 bedrooms with bathrooms, to be used for short-term rentals or weekends; -large rooms already used by the farmhouse, including a large hall with services and equipped kitchens, ideal for catering, events or educational activities. The property combines the charm of the rustic with the comfort of modern renovations, offering multiple opportunities for use: private home, accommodation facility, events or investment. Main features: *14,000 square meters of private land *renovated and ready-to-use building *large and bright spaces *natural and private context Renovated and totally rebuilt in 2011, it is equipped with underfloor heating with a wood boiler that also produces hot water. Furthermore, in 2013, a 19 kW photovoltaic system was installed, there is provision for building a swimming pool and there is an artificial pond for collecting rainwater. A unique opportunity for those who dream of living in the countryside or starting a business in the tourism-hospitality sector.', 'Cocconato', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'strada Vai, 7', 45.08922, 8.04397, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33716983/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/bb/ef/5d/741458644.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/bb/ef/5d/741458644.webp"]', 48, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 58.0, 72.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 61.0, 63.0, 862.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 33.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (166, '32904023', 98000.0, 137.0, 5, 1, 'Villa in frazione Cimaferle, 68', 'Located in a hamlet of the town of Ponzone, a detached house on four sides with a private garden. The property is externally in good condition and internally renovated. On the ground floor there is a large warehouse/cellar. On the raised ground floor: entrance into a living room with fireplace, kitchen, three bedrooms and a bathroom. On the first floor, accessible via an external staircase, there is a spacious and usable attic. Very panoramic and quiet location.', 'Ponzone', 'Alessandria', 'piemonte', 'frazione Cimaferle, 68', 44.5450168, 8.4807231, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32904023/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/e3/3b/42/698854814.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/e3/3b/42/698854814.webp"]', 37, 'villa', 'villa', 58.0, 85.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 53.0, 56.0, 715.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 32.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (167, '33860863', 228000.0, 220.0, 8, 2, 'Villa in via Olivetti, 15', 'Beautiful modern villa, built within a large garden surrounding the residence.  The ground floor consists of the living area with entrance hall, double-height living room with fireplace and mezzanine ideal as a study, spacious kitchen, large patio, two double bedrooms and two bathrooms. In the attic area, accessed from the mezzanine, there are two further bedrooms with a master bathroom and walk-in wardrobe. In the basement, there is a laundry area, cellar and storage room, boiler room and a spacious garage for three cars. The panoramic location is beautifully exposed and guarantees excellent sunlight even in the winter months. The property is in excellent general condition and does not require any renovation.', 'Sparone', 'Torino', 'piemonte', 'via Olivetti, 15', 45.4165336, 7.5416635, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33860863/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/9e/70/e2/733056918.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/9e/70/e2/733056918.webp"]', 41, 'villa', 'villa', 58.0, 56.0, 15.0, 100.0, 54.0, 54.0, 72.0, 1036.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 25.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (168, '33725469', 265000.0, 75.0, 4, 2, 'Detached house in via Petrolla, 70', 'LA CASA DEL PORTO - AN ENCHANTING INDEPENDENT SEASIDE HOME, WITH A PANORAMIC TERRACE OVERLOOKING THE PORT OF VILLANOVA IN OSTUNI Key features: -Independent house of approx. 75 sqm, on the first floor  -Direct view of the port and the sea of Villanova -Spacious panoramic terrace, fully equipped, with 360° views -Kitchen, living area with sofa bed, double bedroom, two bathrooms -Hot/cold air conditioning system -Just steps from beaches, restaurants, and services In one of the most charming stretches of the Apulian Adriatic coast, overlooking the port of Villanova in Ostuni, lies a magical retreat, suspended between sky and sea. This independent residence is a rare gem, set in an area undergoing urban renewal, where the charm of a seaside village meets the comfort of modern living. Located on the first floor of a detached structure, with a wide and comfortable private staircase, the home opens into a bright and airy space, arranged entirely on one level. The living area flows elegantly into an open-plan kitchen, dining space, and a cozy lounge with a sofa bed—perfect for welcoming friends or guests. A spacious and refined double bedroom ensures rest and relaxation, while the two generously sized bathrooms, thoughtfully designed, evoke the tones and textures of the Mediterranean. But it’s when you ascend the second internal staircase that the emotional heart of the home reveals itself: a large panoramic terrace, equipped for sunbathing in every season and for enjoying romantic dinners under the stars, with breathtaking 360-degree views of the sea and port. From here, time seems to slow down—the gentle bobbing of boats, the soothing sound of waves, the light caressing the white stone. Ideal for sea lovers and boat owners, thanks to direct proximity to the port, this property is also perfect as a charming holiday home or as an exclusive hospitality venture, offering guests an authentic and refined experience. The location is strategic: just 10 minutes by car from Ostuni, ', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'via Petrolla, 70', 40.7899867, 17.5865538, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33725469/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d9/80/26/728912594.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d9/80/26/728912594.webp"]', 45, 'independantHouse', 'villa', 57.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 55.0, 84.0, 3533.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 79.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (169, '34477660', 680000.0, 123.0, 6, 2, 'Detached house in via Cattedrale no number', 'The Best-Kept Secret of Ostuni: Luxury Palace with Sea-View Terrace and Jacuzzi Palazzo Perla di Ostuni – Prestigious Independent Terraced House in the Historic Center of the White City Key Features: -Palazzo Perla di Ostuni is an elegant palace in the heart of the historic center. -It is an independent terraced house of 123 sqm. -It features 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with functional design. -The living area includes a fully equipped kitchen and a bright, spacious living room. -The highlight is the panoramic terrace with sea and historic center views. -The terrace also has a private jacuzzi, perfect for relaxation. -The property is renovated with high-end finishes. -Already successfully operated in high-end tourist rentals. In the vibrant heart of Ostuni’s historic center, among white alleys shaped by time and Mediterranean-scented corners, stands Palazzo Perla di Ostuni, a prestigious independent terraced palace that embodies the most authentic and sophisticated essence of the White City. A rare residence, perfectly balancing historic charm with contemporary luxury, designed for those who seek not just a home, but a true experience. With 123 sqm spread over multiple levels, the property offers two bedrooms, two bathrooms, a fully equipped kitchen, and an extraordinary panoramic terrace with jacuzzi. The interiors tell a story of timeless elegance: tufa vaults, exposed stone, original architectural details, and authentic materials merge seamlessly with a refined and functional interior design, ideal for modern living and high-level hospitality. The living area is bright and welcoming, featuring a fully integrated kitchen and an elegant lounge where every element is designed for comfort and style. The sofa bed naturally transforms into a second sleeping area, perfect for private use or luxury tourism. Upstairs, the master bedroom offers an intimate and peaceful retreat, enhanced by an en-suite bathroom with exquisite finishes, where wellbeing becomes part of everyda', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'via Cattedrale no number', 40.7332504, 17.5785873, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34477660/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a9/9e/be/756919703.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/a9/9e/be/756919703.webp"]', 37, 'independantHouse', 'palazzo', 57.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 64.0, 78.0, 5528.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 82.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (170, '32218778', 840000.0, 130.0, 11, 4, 'Villa in contrada Tamburroni no number', 'Elegance and tradition: fine trulli with swimming pool in Ostuni Area 130sqm - Land 10,000€ - 4 bedrooms - 4 bathrooms  Discover the timeless enchantment of Trulli di Pregio con Piscina in Ostuni, an exclusive residence that combines the authenticity of Apulian tradition with contemporary comfort. Immersed in a 10,000 sqm natural park, this extraordinary complex of trulli, completely renovated, is the perfect choice for those who desire a refined retreat in the heart of the Itria Valley, one of the most enchanting areas of Puglia. This prestigious 130-square metre property is spread over a single floor, with large, bright spaces that enhance the beauty of the trulli, while maintaining all modern comforts. The property is already on income, thus offering an excellent investment opportunity for those seeking a residence that can also be a source of income. The double living room, elegant and cosy, becomes the heart of the house, perfect for hosting moments of conviviality. The eat-in kitchen, with its gas and electric hob, two dishwashers, an electric oven and a charming wood-burning oven, lends itself to unforgettable gastronomic experiences. The three double bedrooms and the bedroom with a double bed and a bunk bed, each equipped with exclusive amenities, offer unparalleled peace and quiet. The four bathrooms with shower and bidet are finished with high-quality materials, ensuring a perfect blend of style and practicality. Outside, the large swimming pool and jacuzzi with hot water are surrounded by the lush greenery and breathtaking views of the Ostuni countryside. The surrounding land, with its artesian well and large green spaces, offers endless possibilities to fully experience the beauty of nature, with the opportunity to organise events, relax outdoors or simply enjoy the peace that only this corner of Puglia can offer. Located just a few minutes from the centre of Ostuni, the White City, famous for its charming old town and pristine beaches, this trulli compl', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'contrada Tamburroni no number', 40.730503, 17.646328, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32218778/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/45/c2/3c/677330702.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/45/c2/3c/677330702.webp"]', 75, 'villa', 'villa', 57.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 63.0, 78.0, 6462.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 87.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (171, '34189161', 998000.0, 330.0, 9, 4, 'Villa in via Isola no number', 'This splendid villa is a true corner of paradise, immersed in greenery and surrounded by vineyards, and by a farm that enhances its rustic and charming atmosphere. The entrance on the ground floor welcomes you with a bright living area, characterized by large windows that offer a breathtaking view of the surrounding landscape. The eat-in kitchen, complete with a practical pantry and services, represents the heart of the house, ideal for convivial family dinners. Continuing to the upper floor, there is a cozy living room with a fireplace, which gives warmth and intimacy to the spaces. The sleeping area consists of three bedrooms, each with its own private bathroom, guaranteeing comfort and privacy for all guests. On the S1 floor, the villa offers a tavern with a kitchen, perfect for moments of relaxation and entertainment, along with a living room with a fireplace, which invites you to cozy evenings. There is also a cellar area, ideal for wine lovers. Externally, the villa has a large plot of land that houses a swimming pool, perfect for cooling off during hot summer days, and a porch where you can enjoy pleasant moments outdoors. Parking spaces are easily accessible, making the villa not only a refuge, but also a practical and functional residence. A true dream for those seeking a balance between elegance, comfort and nature. Address purely indicative of the area, in respect and protection of privacy.', 'Luni', 'La Spezia', 'liguria', 'via Isola no number', 44.0724408, 10.0391493, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34189161/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/fb/b2/4c/744731666.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/fb/b2/4c/744731666.webp"]', 30, 'villa', 'villa', 57.0, 42.0, 40.0, 80.0, 60.0, 58.0, 68.0, 3024.0, 'Pisa (PSA)', 52.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (172, '34811148', 698000.0, 550.0, 16, 5, 'Detached house in via Parpaglia, 52', 'Entire Period Building in the Historic Center (only 10 minutes from the beaches) In Oristano, a city in Sardinia close to the sea, whose territory tells ancient stories starting from the very important Phoenician complex of Tharros by the sea (a must-see! ) and continuing through the glorious Giudicale period (Middle Ages) whose traces are still visible today in its historic center, we offer for sale at the very central and private Via Parpaglia 52 a small period palace of 550 SQM free on three sides. The palace is spread over three levels and is composed on the ground floor, with access from the main entrance, of several rooms once used by service personnel with storage and technical rooms, as well as a three-room apartment with independent access; a small warehouse with independent access and a 30 sqm garage. On the first "noble" floor, accessed by an internal staircase, we find 7 rooms with 3 bathrooms, a small terrace, and other technical spaces. On the second attic floor, there are 6 rooms with largely habitable internal heights and to be renovated, and a large terrace on the same level. Oristano is a 10-minute drive from beautiful beaches and the tourist port, and only a 50-minute drive from Cagliari airport via a convenient and fast 4-lane road (SS 131).', 'Oristano', 'Oristano', 'sardegna', 'via Parpaglia, 52', 39.9045017, 8.5930813, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34811148/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/87/b1/d7/770032030.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/87/b1/d7/770032030.webp"]', 35, 'independantHouse', 'house', 57.0, 79.0, 40.0, 60.0, 56.0, 43.0, 55.0, 1269.0, 'Cagliari (CAG)', 83.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (173, '31386505', 490000.0, 360.0, 10, 3, 'Detached house in località Salsominore', 'Single house for sale in Salsomaggiore Terme, Salsominore For sale in Salsomaggiore Terme, in the Salsominore area, spacious house of approximately 360 square meters, in addition to a large attic, two garages, a cellar, large surrounding land, free upon deed. The property is a splendid traditional-style farmhouse, entirely consolidated and renovated between 2009 and 2012, with the recovery of exposed stone and bricks in most of the walls, a new roof with partial recovery of the original tiles. The property is surrounded by greenery, enjoys a splendid position and view, and is just a few minutes, even on foot, from Salsomaggiore Terme and all services. The structure has been The property consists of two houses, with the easy possibility of being reduced to a single house. Each of the two houses has an independent entrance, its own external porch and its own independent land area. The first house is on two floors, consisting of 4 rooms, a kitchen, two bathrooms, is habitable, furnished, with a kitchen and an exposure on three sides, with double-glazed windows and wood, internal coat. The second house is larger, on two floors plus a large wooden attic of over 50 square meters, and consists of 5 rooms, a kitchen, three bathrooms, a boiler room. The second house has been completed in all administrative, structural, wall and service connection aspects, and must be completed with systems, plasters, floors and fixtures. The property also includes a plot of land of approximately 13,000 square meters, a garage, an underground cellar in exposed stone, a portico with three red brick columns, a second garage housed in a separate building with two large porticoes. Ideal for those who want a spacious and comfortable home in a quiet and well-served area. Ace class G. The request is € 490,000. 00 Ref. 66109L.', 'Salsomaggiore Terme', 'Parma', 'emilia-romagna', 'località Salsominore', 44.8343472, 9.9852382, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/31386505/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/3e/59/b1/652225851.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/3e/59/b1/652225851.webp"]', 45, 'independantHouse', 'farmhouse', 57.0, 65.0, 40.0, 40.0, 56.0, 55.0, 67.0, 1361.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 102.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (174, '35120959', 375000.0, 170.0, 8, 3, 'Terraced house in strada Cavo Argine', 'TORRAZZI AREA, Strada Cavo Argine, quiet and residential location bordering a park, END-OF-TERRACE VILLA on three levels, GARDEN on three sides, RENOVATED. (GROUND FLOOR): Porch, garage, bathroom-laundry room, study, and approximately 100 sqm garden. (FIRST FLOOR): Entrance, living room with balcony and fireplace, eat-in kitchen, and bathroom. (SECOND FLOOR): Hallway, three bedrooms (two double and one medium), bathroom, and balcony. On the third floor, an attic for storage with a height of 1.5 meters. INDEPENDENT HEATING. Excellent condition, new air conditioning in all rooms, new electrical and plumbing systems, covered parking spaces in the garden, granite and parquet flooring, ceramic bathrooms, new doors and windows, etc. On the ground floor, it is possible to have a small independent two-room apartment or use it as an independent office-studio. Delivery 6 months from the preliminary sales agreement. PRICE: Euro 375,000.', 'Modena', 'Modena', 'emilia-romagna', 'strada Cavo Argine', 44.6573306, 10.9592683, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/35120959/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/be/d3/75/780889590.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/be/d3/75/780889590.webp"]', 39, 'terracedHouse', 'villa', 57.0, 12.0, 40.0, 100.0, 75.0, 57.0, 72.0, 2206.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 29.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (175, '34042411', 350000.0, 450.0, 10, 5, 'Villa in via Roma Nuova, 140', 'For more information, contact us by phone or by writing to the WhatsApp number 328. 17. 13. 750 Castel Giorgio in a strategic, private location but close to all services, Immersed in the heart of an enchanting hilly landscape, located in the province of Terni, a short distance from Orvieto and near Lake Bolsena and Civita di Bagnoregio, we offer for sale a residence perfect for those looking for a refined villa in the quiet Umbrian countryside. Surrounded by the sounds of nature and with a panoramic view, we discover a place with romantic and luxurious characteristics. With a surface area of 400 square meters, the property welcomes its guests with elegant rooms and large bathrooms, offering every imaginable comfort. The building has been finished with care and elegance, using refined and precious materials, where contemporary furniture and modern finishes can be integrated. The property is surrounded by a lush garden, with various trees and ornamental plants, excellent for summer evenings where you can spend unforgettable moments under a starry sky, perhaps sipping an aperitif together with guests. Also suitable for building a swimming pool. The sun embraces this enchanted place all day long, giving us invigorating sunrises and romantic sunsets. All in a continuous evolution of colors and scents ideal for relaxing or reading a book or doing any recreational activity finding any kind of inspiration. This property is not just a house, but a place of timeless elegance. An unrepeatable opportunity in the prestigious real estate scene, ready to accommodate even Holiday Homes, B&Bs, or facilities for Assisted Healthcare Residences Articulated on several levels, it consists of environments connected to each other through a wonderful wooden staircase. The property consists of five bedrooms, two kitchens, a double representative living room, two dining rooms, a study, four bathrooms and, in the basement, a hobby room with bathroom and several cellar and work rooms as well as', 'Castel Giorgio', 'Terni', 'umbria', 'via Roma Nuova, 140', 42.7039557, 11.9720262, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34042411/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/55/09/90/742955191.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/55/09/90/742955191.webp"]', 31, 'villa', 'villa', 57.0, 72.0, 15.0, 40.0, 54.0, 59.0, 72.0, 778.0, 'Roma FCO', 103.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (176, '33926240', 370000.0, 355.0, 9, 4, 'Villa in via Capra, 20', 'MGRV0078 - FOR INFORMATION AND VIEWINGS CONTACT OUR REAL ESTATE CONSULTANT MARCO AT [PHONE NUMBER] ALSO VIA SMS-WHATSAPP COSSOMBRATO AT - VIA CAPRA 20 We offer a splendid villa surrounded by its green and planted garden, positioned dominantly on top of the hill, allowing for a 360-degree open view and sun all day long! The modern-style property has a total area of 355sqm divided over three levels, while the land and hill of approximately 20sqkm consist of a fenced garden, lawn, woods, and, if desired, space for a future swimming pool. The property was built in 1975 and completely renovated in 2006. The entrance opens onto the large living room and the adjoining eat-in kitchen with access to the porch for convivial summer moments. Five steps lead to the hallway for the bathroom with a shower, to the sleeping area with a large bedroom, walk-in closet, en-suite bathroom with shower, and a small bedroom. Climbing the spiral staircase leads to the open-space attic, currently used as a bedroom with a bathroom and walk-in closet. From the entrance, descending the stairs leads to the basement floor where we find the second living unit, where the large living area opens with an arch onto the eat-in kitchen, bedroom, and bathroom with shower. Laundry room, under-stairs storage, technical room for the boiler, garage. Oak parquet flooring laid diagonally in a herringbone pattern on the ground floor, where in the kitchen, multicolor ceramic tiles echo the style of the balconies. Wood-effect ceramic tiles in the basement. Glass block inserts in the walls to increase the brightness of the rooms. Radiator heating with a condensing boiler. PVC double-glazed windows and mosquito nets. From the road leading to the villa, there is a double entrance with two automated gates in both directions of travel. In front of the villa, the canopy offers convenient space for parking two cars, and at the rear, the structure facilitates tool storage. Septic tank. Rainwater collection well for irriga', 'Cossombrato', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'via Capra, 20', 44.968737, 8.1550337, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33926240/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/4c/05/fa/774756495.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/4c/05/fa/774756495.webp"]', 59, 'villa', 'villa', 57.0, 55.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 59.0, 72.0, 1042.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 47.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (177, '34045683', 74000.0, 110.0, 4, 2, 'Terraced house in via Rocca D''Arazzo', 'Looking for a charming little house for your weekend getaways? We have just what you need! In the sunny town of Montaldo Scarampi, in the province of Asti, set in a panoramic position among rolling vineyard-covered hills, we offer for sale a lovely and welcoming house with all utilities and fully functional. Basement: cellar. Ground floor: entrance/hallway, living room, furnished eat-in kitchen, bathroom, and storage room. First floor: bright furnished bedroom with space for a walk-in closet, bathroom, and balcony overlooking the countryside. A private courtyard completes the property, offering the perfect space to relax outdoors and enjoy the peaceful rhythm of rural life. The house is ready to welcome a family who cherishes the tranquility of the Monferrato region — an area of gentle hills, vineyards, and small villages, recognized as a UNESCO World Heritage Site.', 'Montaldo Scarampi', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'via Rocca D''Arazzo', 44.8325502, 8.2544486, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34045683/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/df/0a/eb/739585967.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/df/0a/eb/739585967.webp"]', 59, 'terracedHouse', 'villa', 57.0, 89.0, 15.0, 60.0, 54.0, 50.0, 58.0, 673.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 63.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (178, '29118893', 170000.0, 173.0, 8, 2, 'Detached house in strada Veirera di Abasse, 117', 'Nestled in over 15,000 sqm of meadow and woodland in a panoramic position with rare independence and no neighboring concerns. This house, built with solid reinforced concrete from foundation to roof, represents an interesting new offering on the Ponzone market. The house has a raw facade and comprises on the ground floor a large garage with various technical rooms with heights and openings suitable for conversion into living space. The first floor, accessed from a perimeter terrace, has a living room, a kitchen, a bathroom, and two double bedrooms. The attic, accessible via a comfortable internal staircase, is ideal for hosting guests, as it is currently used as a relaxation study area, and is equipped with a full bathroom and exceptional views. The village of Cimaferle is a 5-minute drive away. Excellent as a residential solution.', 'Ponzone', 'Alessandria', 'piemonte', 'strada Veirera di Abasse, 117', 44.5537714, 8.4932083, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/29118893/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/c5/5f/b4/611707018.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/c5/5f/b4/611707018.webp"]', 38, 'independantHouse', 'villa', 57.0, 61.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 51.0, 71.0, 983.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 31.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (179, '33668874', 250000.0, 200.0, 7, 2, 'Villa', 'In the hamlet of Moretti, a stone''s throw from the center and amenities, we offer this spacious and panoramic villa, which, due to its location and structure, is well suited for year-round living. Served by a flat and always accessible municipal road, the property has convenient driveway access, a large garage connected to the house, and several parking spaces in the large paved courtyard surrounding the building. A large terracotta-paved portico is the entrance area to the main apartment, which is spread over the first floor on a single level. Immediately, a very bright living room with a fireplace and two French doors provide direct access to the garden on one side and the panoramic terrace on the other, a kitchenette also with access to the terrace, 3 bedrooms, and a large bathroom with a tub and double sink. A spiral staircase internally connects the main house to both the attic, still unfinished but usable for creating additional living space, and the ground floor, partly (30sqm) used as a garage and partly intended as a tavern equipped with a kitchen and a typical wood-burning stove built by a local craftsman, a bedroom, and a bathroom.. . all with direct access to the outside and to the large oven and barbecue area.', 'Ponzone', 'Alessandria', 'piemonte', 'Ponzone', 44.5486712, 8.5223357, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33668874/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/4a/98/db/726139958.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/4a/98/db/726139958.webp"]', 52, 'villa', 'villa', 57.0, 36.0, 15.0, 100.0, 54.0, 65.0, 76.0, 1250.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 29.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (180, '34087973', 1350000.0, 350.0, 13, 5, 'Villa in via U. Giordano no number', 'In the heart of the Area della Cupa, in Monteroni di Lecce, stands a villa that represents one of the most authentic, and at the same time most refined, ways of experiencing Salento. A strategic location that perfectly combines comfort and privacy: the urban centers of Monteroni and Lecce are very close, yet here one breathes a true silence, made of nature, space, and light. Access to the property unfolds through an avenue of pine trees that immediately introduces the atmosphere of the place: you leave the road behind, step into the greenery, and instantly perceive a change of rhythm, of light, of sound. The villa, approximately 350 sqm, is set within 2.2 hectares of private land which also includes a traditional Salento tool house, a tangible expression of local rural heritage. The interiors feature splendid star and barrel vaults, carefully selected materials, and a renovation that has enhanced the original identity while integrating contemporary comforts: every room is equipped with fan coils, while two solar panels on the roof power the heat pumps. Enhancing the living area and several rooms of the house, three stone fireplaces amplify the warm and welcoming atmosphere, providing natural warmth and restoring that sense of authentic comfort that belongs to historic Salento residences. The bedrooms are four, all with private bathrooms; three feature a designer bathtub harmoniously integrated into the suite space. One of the en-suite bedrooms is located in the annex, connected yet independent: here there is also a living room, a study, and a private garden, ideal for hosting guests while ensuring autonomy and privacy. In the main residence, the living area is designed to enhance natural light: the large front window creates visual continuity between interior and exterior, illuminating the living room and kitchen throughout the day. Outside, the two wells represent a concrete added value; every bathroom in the villa is equipped with a shower and authorization has al', 'Monteroni di Lecce', 'Lecce', 'puglia', 'via U. Giordano no number', 40.3230811, 18.0828594, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34087973/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/0a/b8/12/742165280.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/0a/b8/12/742165280.webp"]', 34, 'villa', 'villa', 56.0, 0.0, 40.0, 40.0, 91.0, 71.0, 75.0, 3857.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 144.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (181, '32517482', 1700000.0, 210.0, 7, 6, 'Villa in contrada donnagnora no number', 'Splendid Villa with Pool and Independent Suites a Few Kilometers from Ostuni Immersed in the tranquility of the Apulian countryside, this elegant villa represents an exclusive solution for those seeking a prestigious residence or an opportunity for high-level hospitality activities. Villa Description The property, designed to offer maximum comfort, consists of: Day Area: A spacious kitchen overlooking the garden and the splendid pool area. A cozy living room, characterized by a refined built-in sofa. Night Area: Three double bedrooms, spacious and bright, each with a private bathroom. An additional guest bathroom, located along the main corridor. Independent Suites Adjacent to the villa, there are two private suites, each composed of: A bedroom. A modern bathroom. A functional kitchenette. Both suites offer direct access to the outdoor terrace, which overlooks the suggestive infinity pool. Outdoor Area A designer infinity pool, surrounded by a furnished terrace, ideal for relaxing while enjoying the view of the surrounding landscape. An outdoor kitchen equipped with an induction hob and a shaded dining area, perfect for outdoor dinners. Equipment and Comfort The villa is fully equipped with: Electric gate, to guarantee safety and privacy. Air conditioning system, which ensures a comfortable environment in every season. Alarm system, for maximum tranquility. Photovoltaic system, which offers advanced energy efficiency. Strategic Position Located a few kilometers from the center of Ostuni, the villa combines the serenity of the countryside with the proximity to all essential services and the main tourist attractions of the area. A unique property, ideal for those who want an exclusive residence or who are interested in an investment in the heart of Puglia. Land Description: The land is approximately 15,000 square meters and is flat. Points of Interest: The Municipality of Ostuni is part of the province of Brindisi and is located in the Altosalento area, about 7 km fro', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'contrada donnagnora no number', 40.692749, 17.605486, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32517482/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/22/b9/b5/686498335.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/22/b9/b5/686498335.webp"]', 44, 'villa', 'villa', 56.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 60.0, 78.0, 8095.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 87.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (182, '34310205', 1050000.0, 420.0, 14, 8, 'Casale/cascina in manciano no number', 'Manciano (GR) – In a private and panoramic position, just 10 km from Manciano, portion of a farmhouse for agritourism use of approximately 490 sqm spread over two levels, composed of: • Main apartment of approximately 120 sqm with kitchen, living room, bathroom, storage room and three double bedrooms each with a private bathroom. • Four independent double bedrooms with bathroom, respectively of 17 sqm, 23 sqm and two of 28 sqm. • Two-room apartment of approximately 40 sqm with living room, kitchenette, bathroom, mezzanine with double bed and terrace. • Service rooms intended for reception, breakfast room, kitchen, warehouses, laundry and technical room. The property includes: 30 sqm warehouse, veranda with fireplace, portico, 10x7 m swimming pool, covered car parking, land of approximately 3 hectares with olive grove in production of 150 plants. The property is equipped with underfloor heating with thermo-fireplace, LPG system, solar thermal, air conditioning and 12 kW photovoltaic system. Possibility of purchasing a 101.5 hectare organic farm (ref. AZ369).', 'Manciano', 'Grosseto', 'toscana', 'manciano no number', 42.5882458, 11.5193711, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34310205/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/7e/28/2d/763098170.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/7e/28/2d/763098170.webp"]', 45, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 56.0, 36.0, 40.0, 40.0, 64.0, 66.0, 73.0, 2500.0, 'Roma FCO', 106.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (183, '32483368', 1500000.0, 234.0, 9, 4, 'Casale/cascina in via Cerbaiola no number', 'VOLTERRA - EXCLUSIVE - Gorgeous Tuscan-style stone farmhouse with views of Volterra, swimming pool and large private garden. Description Immersed in the Tuscan hills, the villa is located in a panoramic position overlooking Volterra. The property is on three levels for about 300 sqm. The property consists of 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, equipped with 2 kitchens. On the ground floor: kitchen, living area with fireplace, 2 bedrooms, bathroom and second living area with pellet stove. On the second floor: 2 large double bedrooms with private bathroom, one of them with reading area. On the lower level with access to the pool, there is an openspace with equipped kitchen and fireplace, bathroom with shower, technical room and 5,000-liter tank. It is possible to make a second independent apartment. Outdoor Spaces The garden of about 6,000 sq m, with 40 olive trees, cypresses and two wooden cottages, guarantees absolute tranquility. The 8x4 m pool, 1.40-1.60 m deep, is screened by vegetation for total privacy. Outside is a large covered patio with barbecue. Access is convenient thanks to the automatic gate. present canopy for 3 cars, additional parking and twilight lighting. A 3,000-liter water supply is built into an artificial well. Condition and finishes Elegant villa from 2009, built with materials that respect the local architecture: exposed stone, terracotta, wooden fixtures and rustic details. Equipped with 3 pellet stoves: a main one in the kitchen that also heats the living room, one in the living area and one in the master bedroom. In addition, heat pumps present in all rooms, except bathrooms, with 5 outdoor units connected to 7 splitters for tailored climate comfort. Potential uses Only 7 km from Volterra, the villa is ideal as a main residence or vacation home, in a quiet and reserved area, but close to services. Location Breathtaking views of Volterra and the Tuscan countryside, among fields and cypress trees. Local stores are just minutes away. Access via a wel', 'Volterra', 'Pisa', 'toscana', 'via Cerbaiola no number', 43.4287961, 10.858259, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32483368/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/10/69/87/685562779.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/10/69/87/685562779.webp"]', 66, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 56.0, 0.0, 40.0, 80.0, 64.0, 85.0, 75.0, 6410.0, 'Pisa (PSA)', 47.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (184, '34719012', 596000.0, 185.0, 8, 3, 'Villa in via Lawley', 'BIENTINA – Santa Colomba Semi-detached villa with swimming pool, total privacy and views of the Pisan Mountains. In a splendid hillside location, in the sought-after town of Santa Colomba, we offer for sale a semi-detached villa located on the last stretch of a cul-de-sac: a choice that guarantees maximum privacy, silence and privacy, surrounded by greenery and with a magnificent panoramic view of the Pisan Mountains. We are located in the municipality of Bientina, in an exclusive yet extremely convenient hillside setting: all major services are within about 2 km, with the FI-PI-LI entrance, Pisa Airport and the motorway about 20 minutes away. The house A ready-to-move-in villa, in impeccable condition, equipped with modern comforts and state-of-the-art systems. Ground floor – Living area The entrance leads into a large, bright open space, cleverly divided into: • KITCHEN with peninsula, ideal for breakfasts and informal lunches; DINING area with large fireplace and direct access to a loggia overlooking the garden; LIVING ROOM relaxation area, with a large glass opening that leads directly to the outside; bathroom with window. The large windows provide natural light and an open view of the greenery, making the space welcoming and scenic. First Floor – Sleeping Area Accessible via an elegant staircase covered in exposed pietra serena stone, it consists of: • large hallway with access to the terrace; two double bedrooms, one with a large private terrace; single bedroom; bathroom with window and shower; bathroom with shower. Second Floor – Attic Accessible via a beautiful open wood and steel staircase, this attic-like space is ideal as a guest bedroom, study, or relaxation area. Basement Internally connected to the living area, there is a cellar/tavern containing a second kitchen, laundry room, and shower, perfect for socializing or for more independent use of space. Exterior The villa is surrounded by a well-kept and well-organized garden and park on three sides, with', 'Bientina', 'Pisa', 'toscana', 'via Lawley', 43.6951738, 10.6501507, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34719012/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/97/99/34/766451734.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/97/99/34/766451734.webp"]', 71, 'villa', 'villa', 56.0, 4.0, 40.0, 100.0, 64.0, 73.0, 73.0, 3222.0, 'Pisa (PSA)', 21.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (185, '34937934', 690000.0, 260.0, 4, 2, 'Villa in strada San Lorenzo no number', 'In a quiet and private area, we offer this Villa, composed as follows: Entrance, living room, eat-in kitchen, three bedrooms, and two bathrooms, plus a terrace. The living area is 160 sqm, to which 100 sqm of warehouse/garage should be added. The property is surrounded by a large garden of approximately 2500 sqm with olive trees. An interesting opportunity for those who desire a property immersed in greenery and tranquility, not too far from services. Do not hesitate to contact us for further information and to arrange a no-obligation visit. Ponente Immobiliare Via Roma 153 Via Matteotti 248 Corso Mombello 6 The images and description are purely for informational purposes and do not represent a contractual obligation in any way.', 'Sanremo', 'Imperia', 'liguria', 'strada San Lorenzo no number', 43.8167187, 7.7513827, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34937934/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/83/14/e5/774715900.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/83/14/e5/774715900.webp"]', 20, 'villa', 'villa', 56.0, 55.0, 40.0, 40.0, 74.0, 50.0, 57.0, 2654.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 109.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (186, '34647747', 329000.0, 137.0, 3, 2, 'Semi-detached house in via Stella Polare no number', 'Torre delle Stelle, a tourist resort on the southeastern coast of Sardinia, known for its wonderful beaches and numerous amenities, precisely on Via Stella Polare, in a residential setting surrounded by nature, we offer for sale a newly built semi-detached villa with a swimming pool. The villa, currently under construction, is spread over two levels: the raised ground floor comprises an entrance, an open space with an open-plan kitchen and access to an elegant loggia, a hallway, and a bathroom. The first floor, accessible from both an internal staircase and an external staircase, houses the sleeping area and consists of two bedrooms, served by a bathroom with a window and two large terraces, ideal spaces for enjoying relaxing moments outdoors with a suggestive view of the mountains. The villa, unique of its kind, will have a splendid garden on three sides, fully planted and enhanced by an elegant swimming pool. An ideal solution for those seeking an exclusive home with all comforts, in an oasis of peace between sea and mountains. Parking space available in the private courtyard. Delivery June 2026. First-choice finishes and possibility of customization from the specifications. Three other units are available, with prices starting from €329,000.', 'Maracalagonis', 'Cagliari', 'sardegna', 'via Stella Polare no number', 39.1520424, 9.4023385, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34647747/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/99/49/6c/763797898.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/99/49/6c/763797898.webp"]', 26, 'semidetachedHouse', 'torre', 56.0, 17.0, 40.0, 80.0, 56.0, 69.0, 81.0, 2401.0, 'Cagliari (CAG)', 32.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (187, '32978049', 1090000.0, 357.0, 10, 4, 'Detached house in via dell''Angelo Custode', 'A few minutes from the city center, immersed in the tranquility of the first Bolognese hills, we offer for sale a detached villa of approximately 350 square meters, surrounded by a large private park. The house is spread over three levels, with a functional distribution of spaces that guarantees comfort and maximum livability. On the ground floor is the living area, divided into large, well-defined spaces: the entrance leads to a welcoming living area consisting of a living room and lounge, both characterized by large windows that favor natural light and views of the surrounding greenery. The veranda, directly connected to the living room, is a versatile and enjoyable space in every season, ideal as a relaxation or dining area. The kitchen, separate and habitable, completes the living area offering practicality and functionality. There are also two practical closets and a service bathroom, located near the stairwell that connects the various levels of the house. The sleeping area, located on the upper floor, stands out for the excellent distribution of the rooms, all characterized by large surfaces and excellent brightness. The four bedrooms offer generous and easily customizable spaces. There are three bathrooms, well distributed and comfortable, which guarantee functionality and comfort for all family members. The floor is completed by two additional rooms currently used as studies, but easily adaptable as needed to a walk-in closet, hobby spaces, play area or additional bedrooms. The large internal hallways allow a perfect separation between the various environments, ensuring privacy and tranquility. The property includes a basement consisting of a spacious tavern, ancillary rooms and a generously sized garage. The villa offers spacious and well-distributed environments, with excellent exposure and great privacy, ideal for those seeking comfort, independence and usable outdoor spaces, without sacrificing the convenience of services and the city.', 'Bologna', 'Bologna', 'emilia-romagna', 'via dell''Angelo Custode', 44.460532, 11.3620859, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32978049/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/82/85/38/721804061.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/82/85/38/721804061.webp"]', 90, 'independantHouse', 'villa', 56.0, 0.0, 40.0, 100.0, 90.0, 48.0, 73.0, 3053.0, 'Bologna (BLQ)', 10.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (188, '32357089', 278000.0, 270.0, 11, 3, 'Casale/cascina in frazione Rossi, 33', 'Independent house with swimming pool in the heart of Alta Langa Bossolasco, a small enchanted corner in a panoramic hamlet of Alta Langa, an independent house with a swimming pool and a bright garden. The property extends over 270 square meters distributed over several floors. On the ground floor, a relaxation area with a TV room, a games room, a double bedroom and a bathroom; on the first floor a spacious living room and a kitchen leading onto a panoramic terrace, perfect for summer dinners and quiet moments, with panoramic views of the Alps and the surrounding hills. Completing the floor are two bedrooms, a bathroom and a balcony, while the second attic floor houses a further bedroom and a bathroom. The property also includes a garage, a cellar, a laundry room and other service rooms. The jewel in the crown of the house is undoubtedly the fenced garden of about 3,000 square meters, adorned with a laurel acer hedge and embellished with valuable ornamental plants. The barbecue area, the bocce court, the courtyard paved with interlocking blocks and the swimming pool together create an ideal environment for holidays or weekends dedicated to tranquility and scenic beauty. From an energy point of view, the house has undergone recent refurbishment: double-glazed windows, photovoltaic panels, a latest-generation boiler and even a charging station for electric cars ensure, in a decidedly effective way, sustainable and efficient management of the house. A unique opportunity also as an investment! This holiday home, already generating income, is ready to welcome guests in the tourist rental sector, guaranteeing immediate income without the need for further interventions. Don''t miss this chance! Contact us for more details and to book a visit – perhaps as soon as possible, because opportunities like this don''t come along every day. The Dotta real estate agency has distinguished itself for years in the local area thanks to the extreme seriousness and competence of its staff. I', 'Bonvicino', 'Cuneo', 'piemonte', 'frazione Rossi, 33', 44.507626, 8.0238026, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32357089/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/5b/2e/4a/681924899.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/5b/2e/4a/681924899.webp"]', 19, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 56.0, 56.0, 15.0, 60.0, 54.0, 63.0, 72.0, 1030.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 65.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (189, '34042038', 349000.0, 271.0, 6, 2, 'Detached house in via Trilussa', 'Less than 50 meters from the splendid sandy beach of Torre Mozza, a renowned seaside resort in the Municipality of Ugento, we offer for sale a corner villa consisting of two independent apartments, arranged on two levels, for a total internal area of 231 square meters and approximately 300 square meters of outdoor spaces including courtyards, verandas and porticoes, which guarantee exceptional and hardly replicable liveability so close to the sea. The first floor, with independent access via an external staircase, opens onto a large panoramic portico from which you can enjoy the view of the sea and the coast. The interior houses a large and bright open space, with numerous windows, a separate eat-in kitchen, three bedrooms and a complete bathroom with shower. The ground floor is accessible via a private courtyard of approximately 250 square meters, arranged on three sides and designed to offer privacy and outdoor comfort. The large windows illuminate the open space dedicated to the living area with kitchen and living room, which leads to a hallway and four bedrooms, as well as a bathroom with shower. All rooms are generously windowed, pleasantly ventilated and well distributed. In addition, the property includes the overlying solar area, but with great potential for enhancement: it is possible to equip it with gazebos, outdoor lounges or relaxation areas, to create an exclusive space from which to admire the breathtaking view of the sea and enjoy unforgettable sunsets. Thanks to the important size, the double internal composition, the large outdoor spaces and the location close to the beach, the villa represents an ideal solution for multiple families, but also an excellent real estate investment: it is perfectly suited as a prestigious holiday home, accommodation facility, or for the creation of a commercial or restaurant business in an area of strong tourist appeal. The location is also strategic for quickly reaching seaside resorts such as Lido Marini and Torre S', 'Ugento', 'Lecce', 'puglia', 'via Trilussa', 39.8577486, 18.1666387, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34042038/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/ff/0e/54/739389420.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/ff/0e/54/739389420.webp"]', 49, 'independantHouse', 'torre', 55.0, 43.0, 40.0, 20.0, 60.0, 56.0, 77.0, 1288.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 186.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (190, '34769989', 1500000.0, 260.0, 8, 3, 'Villa in strada Provinciale 28 no number', 'Farmhouse with swimming pool, guesthouse, and equipped outdoor spaces in Ostuni - Immersed in the tranquility of the Apulian countryside, this refined farmhouse offers a total surface area of 260 sqm, designed to combine authentic charm, modern technology, and total living comfort. The property is surrounded by a large, meticulously maintained garden, enhanced by a private swimming pool, a mini whirlpool, and perfectly equipped relaxation areas. Interior Layout First Floor – approximately 180 sqm The main level is distinguished by its brightness, attention to detail in the finishes, and rooms designed for harmonious living with the outdoor spaces. It includes: Three bedrooms Two bathrooms Spacious and functional living room-kitchen Laundry room Changing room This configuration creates an elegant and perfectly organized environment, ideal for families or those who desire airy and well-distributed spaces. Ground Floor – approximately 80 sqm An independent unit that guarantees versatility and privacy, ideal as a guest apartment, staff quarters, or as a self-contained area within the property. It includes: One bedroom Veranda Entrance/dining area with kitchen Bathroom and ante-bathroom Outdoor Areas and Comfort The outdoor spaces are one of the property''s strong points: Private swimming pool with solarium area Mini whirlpool Large English lawn with irrigation system Two verandas totaling approximately 150 sqm Equipped pergola and outdoor dining area Barbecue in the pool area Wood-fired oven on the veranda LED lighting for atmospheric evenings Features and Services Air conditioning in all bedrooms Underfloor heating with heat pump Thermally broken windows and doors 20 kW photovoltaic system Artesian well with 380 V pump Alarm system and video surveillance (CCTV) Automatic gate with batteries Covered parking spaces with charging station for electric cars Fiber optic internet connection Potential Developments: This farmhouse is an ideal solution for those seeking an elegan', 'Ostuni', 'Brindisi', 'puglia', 'strada Provinciale 28 no number', 40.7202273, 17.5774469, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34769989/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/1c/3c/52/768442159.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/1c/3c/52/768442159.webp"]', 29, 'villa', 'farmhouse', 55.0, 0.0, 40.0, 60.0, 92.0, 60.0, 71.0, 5769.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 83.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (191, '33195258', 1300000.0, 142.0, 4, 2, 'Villa in contrada Capitolo', 'In Capitolo, the most exclusive coastal area of Monopoli, we present for sale a newly built contemporary villa that blends architectural elegance, advanced comfort, and certified sustainability. Nestled in absolute tranquility and just a short walk from the sea, this residence represents a rare opportunity for those looking to live or invest in one of the most sought-after destinations in Apulia. Completed in 2024, the villa is certified Class A4 under the ITACA protocol, the highest standard in energy efficiency and environmental quality. It is fully electric, gas-free, and equipped with cutting-edge systems including controlled mechanical ventilation, thermal and acoustic insulation, photovoltaic and solar panels. The result is a quiet, highly efficient home with minimal environmental impact and extremely low maintenance costs, ideal for year-round living. The interior opens onto a spacious living room with open-plan kitchen and triple panoramic glass windows overlooking the garden and the underground whirlpool pool, offering seamless visual continuity between indoor and outdoor spaces. The sleeping area features three bedrooms, including two doubles, a luxurious master bathroom finished with premium materials, and a second full bathroom. The property is completed by a refined full-electric outdoor kitchen and a large sea-view terrace, perfect for enjoying the light, sea breeze, and sunsets over the Adriatic. A beautifully landscaped private garden surrounds the home, ensuring privacy and a deep connection with nature. The villa is sold fully furnished with custom interiors, ready to move in. A perfect luxury second home or a secure and appreciating investment, in a context of high international demand. The combination of location, design, performance, and construction quality makes this a rare real estate opportunity, destined to retain and grow in value over time. For further information, contact Pregio Immobiliare or visit us in our offices in Piazza Milite Ign', 'Monopoli', 'Bari', 'puglia', 'contrada Capitolo', 40.8993953, 17.362532, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33195258/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/b7/3c/37/709121836.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/b7/3c/37/709121836.webp"]', 27, 'villa', 'villa', 55.0, 0.0, 40.0, 80.0, 83.0, 65.0, 71.0, 9155.0, 'Bari (BRI)', 57.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (192, '34380999', 850000.0, 300.0, 13, 2, 'Casale/cascina in via di Ciliano, 37', 'In Tuscany, in the Municipality of Montepulciano, in a quiet and panoramic area, an agricultural estate is for sale, consisting of: Farmhouse built in 1975 with two independent apartments, an agricultural shed of 130 sqm. Surrounding land of approximately 5,000 sqm with a garden, 95 olive trees, and 4.2 hectares of owned vineyard, plus 3.5 hectares of land with leased vineyard. The farmhouse, perfectly habitable, was partially renovated in the 2000s, while the agricultural shed, currently used as equipment storage and workshop, can be renovated to build a winery or a guesthouse. The owned vineyards, in full production, were planted partly in 2006 and partly in 2019, and are fully mechanizable. Various registrations, DOCG DOC IGT. The leased land, with a contract until 12/31/2030, consists of: vineyard for 9,000 sqm, planted in 2019, and arable land for 26,000 sqm. Possibility of separate purchase of: vineyard cultivation equipment, workshop equipment, wine label, and home furnishings. The property also considers the possibility of selling only the farmhouse with guesthouse and surrounding land with olive trees (total 5,000 sqm) and/or selling only the vineyards, and/or only the farmhouse. Price negotiable.', 'Montepulciano', 'Siena', 'toscana', 'via di Ciliano, 37', 43.096304, 11.7843632, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34380999/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/58/86/7a/752413406.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/58/86/7a/752413406.webp"]', 23, 'casalicascine', 'casale', 55.0, 21.0, 40.0, 60.0, 86.0, 56.0, 63.0, 2833.0, 'Firenze (FLR)', 92.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (193, '34249902', 790000.0, 332.0, 10, 4, 'Detached house in via Castiglioni no number', 'ANSELMO, MONTESPERTOLI, Terraced house for sale of 332 Sq. mt. , Excellent Condition, Heating Individual heating system, Energetic class: G, placed at Ground on 1, composed by: 10 Rooms, Separate kitchen 4 Bedrooms, 4 Bathrooms, Garden, Price: € 790,000.', 'Montespertoli', 'Firenze', 'toscana', 'via Castiglioni no number', 43.6887701, 11.0775919, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34249902/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/92/48/20/746993050.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/92/48/20/746993050.webp"]', 58, 'independantHouse', 'house', 55.0, 42.0, 40.0, 100.0, 64.0, 45.0, 56.0, 2380.0, 'Firenze (FLR)', 17.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (194, '34540879', 1400000.0, 483.0, 13, 5, 'Detached house in via Gamberaia no number', 'Immersed in the rolling hills south of Florence, in a dominant and private position, this extraordinary portion of a charming farmhouse stands out for its timeless appeal and its harmonious integration with the surrounding natural landscape. The property is enveloped by a large terraced garden that opens like a true balcony over the greenery, offering enchanting views and an atmosphere of absolute tranquillity. Passing through the entrance gate, a path leads to a clearing adorned with an elegant water-lily pond, from which one can admire the impressive stone structure of the farmhouse, whose origins date back to the year 1000. The outdoor spaces, meticulously maintained, are enhanced by well-equipped areas and a refined selection of Mediterranean vegetation, creating a setting of remarkable charm. The residence is arranged over two levels, connected both internally and externally, offering a layout that is functional yet highly evocative. On the ground floor, a sequence of reception and convivial spaces unfolds: a spacious double living room with fireplace, a distinctive kitchen featuring Sicilian majolica-tiled walls and a reclaimed raw marble sink, a private dining room, a second dining room, two sitting rooms, the atmospheric former bread oven room, as well as a guest bathroom and a storage room. The upper floor hosts the sleeping area, comprising four double bedrooms, a large walk-in wardrobe room, four bathrooms, and two terraces—one of which is recessed—ideal for moments of relaxation overlooking the surrounding countryside. The interiors preserve materials and finishes of exceptional quality: handmade terracotta floors in the bedrooms and reclaimed terracotta in the living areas; ceilings with exposed beams and bricks, treated in warm blond walnut tones or whitewashed with lime; walls partly left with rustic exposed stone and partly plastered and painted in soft natural hues of beige, ivory, and pale yellow. The large glass enclosure of the portico, custom-ma', 'Bagno a Ripoli', 'Firenze', 'toscana', 'via Gamberaia no number', 43.7178576, 11.37863, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34540879/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d2/fa/87/759560116.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/d2/fa/87/759560116.webp"]', 40, 'independantHouse', 'farmhouse', 55.0, 18.0, 40.0, 100.0, 64.0, 70.0, 63.0, 2899.0, 'Firenze (FLR)', 17.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (195, '34866882', 830000.0, 246.0, 6, 2, 'Villa in Imperia', 'Villa Limoni - Located on the enchanting hills of Imperia, in the heart of the prestigious Riviera dei Fiori, this splendid villa with swimming pool offers breathtaking sea views. Nestled on a sprawling 2,600 square meter plot, Villa Limoni combines the charm of Liguria''s natural beauty and the beauty of the sea with refined comfort. It''s the ideal place for those seeking privacy and tranquility, yet still close to the coast and the city, thanks also to its modern, energy-efficient systems (Class A1) and air conditioning.  The upper floor welcomes us to a spacious and bright living room with a fireplace that creates a pleasant atmosphere for relaxing moments. On one side are the dining room and the well-equipped and functional kitchen, complete with a pantry. There''s also room for a secluded and quiet study, as well as a convenient laundry room for household needs. On the other side is the sleeping area: it consists of two bedrooms, a hallway with built-in wardrobes, and two bathrooms. The entire floor is surrounded by a porch and large terraces with outdoor seating areas, tables, and chairs, perfect for al fresco breakfasts or romantic evenings, relaxing in the shade or in the sun: you can choose the setting, but the picture is always a sea view!  An internal staircase from the living room leads to the lower level, a versatile and comfortable space where a second living room is perfect for dinners with friends and family, thanks also to the adjacent kitchenette, which offers additional convenience. A large storage room provides storage for all your necessities. The shaded and private front porch is the ideal place to relax at sunset, admiring the surrounding landscape from the comfort of its interior.  The swimming pool is perfectly integrated into the property, and several sun terraces have been created, equipped with sun loungers and deckchairs for every comfort level, in the sun or shade, offering endless possibilities for entertainment. The garden also features', 'Imperia', 'Imperia', 'liguria', 'Imperia', 43.8889006, 8.0387026, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/34866882/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f5/79/8e/771874951.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/f5/79/8e/771874951.webp"]', 61, 'villa', 'villa', 55.0, 30.0, 40.0, 60.0, 60.0, 69.0, 69.0, 3374.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 86.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (196, '31515862', 280000.0, 176.0, 10, 3, 'Semi-detached house in Sa Lumenera no number', 'Magomadas, in "Sa Lumenera" area, on the central western coast of Sardinia, at two minutes to the beach and five to Bosa, in a privileged panoramic position, quiet and private area, surrounded by typical green and lush Mediterranean plants, as well as the numerous olive groves and vineyards that enrich the surrounding area with wonderful shapes, colours and shades. In this particularly bright and joyful territory, rich in scents, sensations and positive emotions, we offer for sale two independent residential units attached on one side, with the possibility of being connected to each other, in good condition, with a large and private driveway courtyard and spacious verandas with enchanting views over the sea and the surrounding countryside. The apartments are composed as follows: 1) large veranda in front of the entrance, large living room with comfortable dining room, two bathrooms, two double bedrooms, storage, kitchenette and covered veranda, equipped to eat outside with an amazing sea view. 2) large veranda in front of the entrance, living room, large dining room with kitchen area, two double bedrooms, bathroom, covered veranda that can be equipped for outdoor dining with wonderful views over the sea and the surrounding countryside. The apartments will be sold furnished.', 'Magomadas', 'Oristano', 'sardegna', 'Sa Lumenera no number', 40.2692532, 8.4832176, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/31515862/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/cb/2c/c0/655963891.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/cb/2c/c0/655963891.webp"]', 61, 'semidetachedHouse', 'house', 55.0, 62.0, 40.0, 40.0, 56.0, 42.0, 70.0, 1591.0, 'Olbia (OLB)', 112.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (197, '32171817', 450000.0, 224.0, 10, 3, 'Villa', '**Detached Villa in a unique position with olive grove, vineyard and amazing sea view. Discover this magnificent recently built detached villa located in an area of incomparable beauty, immersed in a land of over 9,000 square meters and surrounded by the colourful Mediterranean scrub. The property has an olive grove with more than 50 trees in production and a vineyard that offers different qualities of good wines such as Malvasia, Cannonau, Sangiovese as well as different qualities of fine dessert grapes, much appreciated by lovers of nature and good wine. The house is on two levels connected both internally and externally, offering on the ground floor a spacious and well-lit rustic kitchen, hallway, two bedrooms, bathroom, large covered veranda in front of the entrance and spacious ventilated inspectable gap, large external room of approximately 45 square meters used as a tool shed with a kitchenette and barbeque, very spacious courtyard surrounding the house with several parking spaces; fence made with handcrafted dry stone walls and wrought iron gate. The first floor welcomes us with a small hallway, kitchen-dining room, two bathrooms, three bedrooms, large terrace with wonderful views over the sea and the surrounding countryside ideal for dinners at sunset. At the back of the house there is a large above ground swimming pool (5 x 10 m²) ideal for cooling off during hot summer days. Photovoltaic system, advanced heating and cooling system, together with the 300-liter solar boiler, guarantees comfort all year round. A well and a 13,000-liter collection tank ensure water for irrigation and domestic use, while a water softener improves the quality of the water. With a commercial surface of 224 m² and an internal surface of 187 m², this villa is a unique opportunity to live in harmony with nature without sacrificing modern luxury and comfort. Don''t miss the chance to own a piece of Paradise!', 'Magomadas', 'Oristano', 'sardegna', 'Magomadas', 40.2567724, 8.4964001, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/32171817/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/33/55/47/676621281.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/33/55/47/676621281.webp"]', 57, 'villa', 'villa', 55.0, 38.0, 40.0, 40.0, 56.0, 66.0, 75.0, 2009.0, 'Olbia (OLB)', 112.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (198, '30167349', 455000.0, 510.0, 15, 8, 'Villa in via mu', 'Prestigious Historic Villa with Private Park – Saliceto (CN) In a strategic location between Liguria and Piedmont, we offer for sale an important manor house nestled in the hills of Saliceto (CN), just 18 km from the Millesimo toll booth – A6 Turin/Savona. The property spans approximately 500 square meters distributed over three levels, served by an internal elevator, and is surrounded by a large private park with access from an elegant tree-lined avenue, guaranteeing privacy, prestige, and potential appreciation. Internal distribution: Eat-in kitchen with fireplace Large and bright triple living room with fireplace Dedicated dining room 13 bedrooms 8 bathrooms Triple garage 2 cellars and service rooms Inside the park there are large secondary buildings, ideal for the construction of outbuildings, staff housing, or accommodation facilities (B&Bs, relais, tourist-accommodation activities). Condition and features: Steel window frames Double-glazed windows Good structural condition Restoration and system upgrades are necessary, with a high margin for revaluation Energy class: E Ideal for: Investors Tourist-accommodation projects Representative residence Real estate development operations A unique property in terms of size, context, and potential, difficult to replicate on the market.', 'Saliceto', 'Cuneo', 'piemonte', 'via mu', 44.41373, 8.1694791, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/30167349/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/7a/2e/63/614749133.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/7a/2e/63/614749133.webp"]', 20, 'villa', 'villa', 55.0, 69.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 47.0, 61.0, 892.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 53.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (199, '33140212', 485000.0, 450.0, 16, 6, 'Detached house in via Bricco Cisero', 'Located in the hills of the Monferrato, this typical L-shaped Piedmontese farmhouse dating back to the 1700s (approximately 450 sqm) features a large internal courtyard garden, accessed through a charming double entrance for vehicles and pedestrians. The main residential unit consists of: Ground floor, overlooking the internal courtyard-garden: an entrance/hallway, a sitting room, a functional kitchen (furnished and included in the price) with an island, a pantry, a large and bright living room, a hallway/anteroom, a bathroom, and the cellar (a tavern-style room with a furnished kitchen included in the price). Ground floor, overlooking the rear courtyard: a veranda, a woodshed, a bathroom, a boiler room, a technical room for the heating system, and a spacious storage area for machinery and agricultural equipment. First floor: 3 bedrooms with separate access, 3 bathrooms, a characteristic hayloft (open portico) with 3 classic exposed brick arches, 2 terraces and a balcony that enjoy a splendid panoramic view. On the right side of the main house, overlooking the internal courtyard-garden, there is a functional dépendance (an excellent, very new building currently used as a workshop) consisting of 3 rooms, 3 bathrooms and a storage room. Opposite the main house, overlooking the internal courtyard-garden, there is a classic independent rustic outbuilding, with a portico on the ground floor and a hayloft on the first floor. The land, in a single plot along with the buildings, totaling 27,320 sqm (currently used as meadowland). Distances from the property: 1.5 km from the village center of Cortandone (AT), 13 km from the Asti Ovest exit of the Turin–Piacenza motorway, 12 km from the Golf Feudo di Asti courses, 37 km from Alba and 45 km from Turin. In addition to being used as a single-family or two-family home, the property is also suitable for an agriturismo, B&B, farmstay, educational farm and/or equestrian facility. Features: Solar panels for hot water production Plumb', 'Cortandone', 'Asti', 'piemonte', 'via Bricco Cisero', 44.9532122, 8.0569939, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33140212/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/3b/9f/dd/714285962.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/3b/9f/dd/714285962.webp"]', 149, 'independantHouse', 'farmhouse', 55.0, 52.0, 15.0, 80.0, 54.0, 55.0, 69.0, 1078.0, 'Torino (TRN)', 42.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
INSERT INTO properties (id, external_id, price, size, rooms, bathrooms, title, description, town, province, region, address, latitude, longitude, url, lead_photo, photos, photos_count, raw_type, property_type, composite_score, value_score, sea_score, airport_score, location_score, character_score, social_potential_score, price_per_sqm, nearest_airport, airport_distance_km, distance_to_sea_km, status, batch_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (200, '33400813', 250000.0, 220.0, 7, 3, 'Villa in Sp210, 39', 'Exclusive villa with a 4,000 sqm park – ample space and privacy In a private setting surrounded by greenery, we offer for sale a splendid detached villa surrounded by a planted and illuminated park of 4,000 sqm, ideal for those seeking tranquility, nature and generous spaces. The property is spread over four levels, composed as follows: Ground floor: entrance from a large livable terrace, connected to a second terrace with direct views of the park. Internally we find a large living room, dining room, eat-in kitchen and a scenic wooden staircase, which gives warmth and character to the environment. First floor: three bedrooms and a bathroom with window. The two double bedrooms overlook a panoramic balcony, perfect for enjoying the view and the silence of the surrounding greenery. Attic floor: large attic room with a second bathroom, ideal as a study, hobby room or guest suite. Basement floor (accessible only from the outside): large double garage, independent apartment consisting of kitchen, dining room, bedroom, bathroom and technical room. Ideal solution for hosting family members or for creating an autonomous area for collaborators. A property to see, where elegance meets functionality.', 'Ponzone', 'Alessandria', 'piemonte', 'SP210, 39', 44.5408222, 8.536827, 'https://www.idealista.it/immobile/33400813/', 'https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/ca/03/13/716409856.webp', '["https://img4.idealista.it/blur/480_360_mq/0/id.pro.it.image.master/ca/03/13/716409856.webp"]', 51, 'villa', 'villa', 55.0, 47.0, 15.0, 100.0, 54.0, 51.0, 70.0, 1136.0, 'Genova (GOA)', 28.0, NULL, 'qualified', '2026-03-12', '2026-03-12 17:35:14', '2026-03-12 17:35:14');
